01:02:06.338 --> 01:02:09.396
mostly schemes that were operated
by the previous government

1181222762
01:02:09.397 --> 01:02:11.553
and will come forward with proposals soon.

3241763334
01:02:11.554 --> 01:02:12.556
>> Panel questions.

1807667935
01:02:12.557 --> 01:02:15.216
>> My condolences to
the Secretary of State as well.

3608336207
01:02:15.217 --> 01:02:17.775
He will be familiar with
the Russian backed Aquind

1057006937
01:02:17.776 --> 01:02:19.929
application for a submarine interconnector

4196237298
01:02:19.931 --> 01:02:22.387
that will cut through
Portsmouth Naval Dockyard,

4155887352
01:02:22.388 --> 01:02:24.242
affecting my constituency to France.

4008362921
01:02:24.243 --> 01:02:27.401
The Ministry of Defence has raised
national security concerns.

941717052
01:02:27.402 --> 01:02:29.911
We've been waiting for
over a year for a decision

3927488340
01:02:29.911 --> 01:02:32.836
on the application from
the Secretary of State.

4148864848
01:02:32.837 --> 01:02:34.041
When will he issue one?

187352239
01:02:34.042 --> 01:02:35.280
>> No, sir.

1371858325
01:02:35.281 --> 01:02:37.791
>> Well, first of all, can
I thank the right hon.

3431584366
01:02:37.792 --> 01:02:39.699
Lady for her kind words about my mum?

760988223
01:02:39.700 --> 01:02:42.257
She will know that,
unfortunately, I can't comment

2695382700
01:02:42.258 --> 01:02:44.362
on the progress of planning applications,

3733849000
01:02:44.364 --> 01:02:47.434
but I will definitely pass on
her comments to my department.

3903775505
01:02:47.435 --> 01:02:47.936
>> Right.

570969910
01:02:47.937 --> 01:03:11.677
We'll let the front bench change Come

3513057954
