to the Urgent Question Helen Whately.

3375834678
01:03:15.630 --> 01:03:15.931
over.

2394491636
01:03:15.932 --> 01:03:17.837
To the Urgent Question Helen Whately.

2982021711
01:03:17.838 --> 01:03:18.741
>> Thank you, Mr.

2589185451
01:03:18.742 --> 01:03:19.192
Speaker.

3046651335
01:03:19.193 --> 01:03:19.946
>> To ask the.

2218463375
01:03:19.947 --> 01:03:23.742
