a statement on the publication

2265528242
01:03:23.743 --> 01:03:28.334
of the Milburn report into
Young People and Work.

1716140133
01:03:28.335 --> 01:03:29.688
>> Minister thank you, Mr.

2484269105
01:03:29.690 --> 01:03:30.140
Speaker.

2815532274
01:03:30.141 --> 01:03:33.184
>> Last week, Alan Milburn
produced a powerful report

3270856868
01:03:33.185 --> 01:03:35.692
on the crisis of opportunity
facing young people.

2376865576
01:03:35.830 --> 01:03:39.737
The Secretary of State asked
him to lead this work because

734842426
01:03:39.739 --> 01:03:43.733
it is a crisis that has been
ignored for far too long,

2996046361
01:03:43.734 --> 01:03:47.286
where far too many young
people are leaving education

2460306850
01:03:47.288 --> 01:03:50.280
and not getting the chance to work.

1931359045
01:03:50.281 --> 01:03:54.492
The human and financial impact on
individuals can last a lifetime,

3039389425
01:03:54.493 --> 01:03:56.982
and the economic costs are significant.

4007699910
01:03:56.983 --> 01:04:00.903
What is clear is that this is not
a feature of the last year or two,

1571205848
01:04:00.904 --> 01:04:04.237
but a deep seated and long term issue.

2121252383
01:04:04.237 --> 01:04:06.832
But unlike the party opposite, Mr.

2345506199
01:04:06.833 --> 01:04:09.434
Speaker, we will not
stand back and abandon

3141753108
01:04:09.435 --> 01:04:12.230
young people in the face of this crisis.

4048366862
01:04:12.231 --> 01:04:14.137
During their last few years in power,

3245132893
01:04:14.138 --> 01:04:16.890
the number of young
people not in education,

2468633204
01:04:19.838 --> 01:04:22.597
employment or training rose
by a quarter of a million.

1879532776
01:04:22.598 --> 01:04:23.550
A shameful legacy.

3421947889
01:04:23.551 --> 01:04:25.857
Rather than holding young
people in contempt.

2728538649
01:04:25.858 --> 01:04:28.780
We believe in them and we
are making opportunity

597935580
01:04:28.781 --> 01:04:30.536
for young people a national cause.

463685428
01:04:30.536 --> 01:04:33.648
We have begun with the Youth Guarantee.

4089452567
01:04:33.649 --> 01:04:37.688
More work experience, workplace
training and apprenticeships.

301694901
01:04:37.829 --> 01:04:40.186
Hiring bonuses for employers
who take on young

3697453591
01:04:40.837 --> 01:04:42.992
people in regular or apprenticeship roles,

635217156
01:04:42.993 --> 01:04:45.786
and subsidised employment for young people

666672260
01:04:45.788 --> 01:04:49.992
who remain out of work for 18 months.

1407723202
01:04:49.993 --> 01:04:50.695
In total, Mr.

3415169058
01:04:50.696 --> 01:04:55.133
Speaker, half a million opportunities
for young people to work,

3452104923
01:04:55.134 --> 01:04:56.937
train or undertake apprenticeships.

3769400964
01:04:56.938 --> 01:04:59.594
We have undertaken welfare
reform to remove barriers

3233062767
01:04:59.596 --> 01:05:01.903
in the benefit system
that trap young people.

2951783881
01:05:01.904 --> 01:05:04.890
We have changed the law
so claimants on sickness

2364492002
01:05:04.891 --> 01:05:07.592
and disability benefits have the right

2414401328
01:05:07.593 --> 01:05:09.900
to try work without
the fear of automatically

1175937331
01:05:09.901 --> 01:05:11.654
triggering a benefit reassessment.

1549323495
01:05:11.655 --> 01:05:13.862
We have narrowed
the gap between the health

3209013684
01:05:13.862 --> 01:05:15.466
element and standard allowance,

3182439619
01:05:15.467 --> 01:05:18.174
a perverse incentive of
the last government's making,

1968472395
01:05:18.175 --> 01:05:23.284
and we are investing in genuinely
personalised employment support.

2558524956
01:05:23.285 --> 01:05:23.485
Mr.

1413923271
01:05:23.486 --> 01:05:25.292
speaker, we have made a good start,

3966925797
01:05:25.834 --> 01:05:29.190
but last week's interim
report is a call to action.

3997273336
01:05:29.191 --> 01:05:31.398
That is why this
government is putting work

2906089394
01:05:31.399 --> 01:05:34.146
and opportunity at
the heart of everything we do,

4238904763
01:05:34.147 --> 01:05:37.987
and we will go even further
as Alan Milburn's work on

1605705201
01:05:37.987 --> 01:05:41.286
his final report
and recommendations come forward.

1340832315
01:05:41.288 --> 01:05:42.691
>> Helen Whately Secretary.

4170415175
01:05:42.692 --> 01:05:43.594
>> Thank you, Mr.

967311781
01:05:43.837 --> 01:05:47.298
Speaker, and I am grateful to you
for granting this urgent question.

1608651382
01:05:47.299 --> 01:05:49.841
It's a shame the Minister
had to be dragged here.

2305606429
01:05:49.842 --> 01:05:52.490
The Secretary of State
was only too eager to

1579154029
01:05:52.491 --> 01:05:55.388
talk about this last week on the telly.

955251520
01:05:55.389 --> 01:05:56.543
But where is he today?

754244939
01:05:56.544 --> 01:06:00.044
Why so quiet now?

271501531
01:06:00.045 --> 01:06:03.056
I think we all know because
the Secretary of State has been

1524871801
01:06:03.057 --> 01:06:06.041
caught out telling the devastating
truth about Labour MPs.

269023414
01:06:06.042 --> 01:06:10.043
Who can we tax in order to
pay benefits to others?

1776409104
01:06:10.044 --> 01:06:12.538
That is what Labour MPs really think.

2916490494
01:06:12.539 --> 01:06:15.137
That is what this government has done.

587919787
01:06:15.138 --> 01:06:17.445
Put up people's taxes,
spent more on benefits

2736014849
01:06:17.446 --> 01:06:21.338
and left hard working people
with less to live off.

1578507864
01:06:21.339 --> 01:06:24.349
And once again, their shenanigans
are getting in the way of

229525777
01:06:24.350 --> 01:06:27.308
something we really should be
talking about every morning.

2511221113
01:06:27.309 --> 01:06:29.745
A million young people wake up in Britain

3131532427
01:06:29.746 --> 01:06:33.188
with nothing to do and nowhere to go.

769492293
01:06:33.190 --> 01:06:36.288
This is a disaster for our
country, our economy,

1640411436
01:06:36.289 --> 01:06:38.597
and worst of all, for
all those young people.

2728595064
01:06:40.839 --> 01:06:42.141
Labour's lost generation.

846848935
01:06:42.142 --> 01:06:45.991
The Minister said this started under us.

2094573492
01:06:45.992 --> 01:06:49.242
Yes, the numbers did start
going up from the pandemic,

1307840612
01:06:49.243 --> 01:06:52.947
so this wasn't a surprise for them.

1780001908
01:06:52.949 --> 01:06:55.496
Yet here we are after
almost two years of them

3208879777
01:06:55.496 --> 01:06:57.504
in office and Labour still has no plan.

1302634552
01:06:57.838 --> 01:07:02.184
All they have done is
make the situation worse.

213811038
01:07:02.185 --> 01:07:04.341
And of course, commission this big report.

91378290
01:07:04.342 --> 01:07:06.295
I welcome Alan Milburn's contribution.

1900835680
01:07:06.297 --> 01:07:10.294
It is a serious analysis,
but Milburn himself says this.

2876105577
01:07:10.295 --> 01:07:11.447
It's just a diagnosis.

1809614639
01:07:11.449 --> 01:07:16.393
There are no solutions here,
no actual answers or policies.

3933438634
01:07:16.394 --> 01:07:19.806
In fact, he even tells us the things
the government has been doing.

3205407996
01:07:19.840 --> 01:07:22.347
Their piecemeal programmes
are not going to work.

370440614
01:07:22.876 --> 01:07:25.133
He also says after six
months of inactivity,

2917477957
01:07:26.795 --> 01:07:29.154
young people are far less
likely to ever work.

585080745
01:07:29.155 --> 01:07:33.754
This is urgent,
but where is their urgency?

2423313951
01:07:33.755 --> 01:07:40.539
Yes, this is not the first time
Labour have let down a young people.

2695005135
01:07:40.540 --> 01:07:44.137
NEETs soared to 17% after Labour's
last stint in government.

750011182
01:07:44.138 --> 01:07:50.499
Conservatives turn that around
to less than 10% in 2019.

1459792324
01:07:50.500 --> 01:07:55.391
Of course, Covid undermined that
progress, but the Labour government

2331376652
01:07:55.392 --> 01:07:57.899
has turned a post-pandemic
problem into a crisis.

2529658184
01:07:57.900 --> 01:08:00.207
Taxing jobs, tying up
businesses in red tape,

255539998
01:08:00.208 --> 01:08:03.541
making it riskier and more
expensive to hire a young person,

1544949771
01:08:03.542 --> 01:08:07.590
