of jobs in retail and hospitality.

636060439
01:08:07.591 --> 01:08:11.390
Like many young people, one of my first
jobs was working in a local pub,

3645540885
01:08:11.391 --> 01:08:16.499
but they've pulled the plug on that
opportunity for this generation.

62079943
01:08:16.500 --> 01:08:20.091
Whenever we do get to hear their
plans, I think we know what they will

3798124913
01:08:20.092 --> 01:08:23.691
be spending more money and taxing
people more to pay for that.

774677747
01:08:23.692 --> 01:08:24.594
The wrong answer.

1294965648
01:08:24.594 --> 01:08:27.002
The answer is jobs back,
businesses, cut taxes,

1303664155
01:08:27.003 --> 01:08:29.813
get rid of red tape, get
government out of the way and.

1758664323
01:08:29.815 --> 01:08:31.250
Reform welfare.

3927426122
01:08:31.251 --> 01:08:32.304
>> It's two minutes.

2048098165
01:08:32.304 --> 01:08:33.007
We've got to.

2505698215
01:08:33.008 --> 01:08:34.795
Yes, it is two minutes.

1872809226
01:08:34.795 --> 01:08:36.300
It's always been two minutes.

20280964
01:08:36.301 --> 01:08:37.705
I've not changed the rules.

3564454773
01:08:37.706 --> 01:08:40.545
When I grant it, please
stick to within the rules.

3903995310
01:08:40.547 --> 01:08:42.554
It helps me because we said we're going

1836551197
01:08:42.554 --> 01:08:45.193
