3763776297
01:08:57.103 --> 01:09:01.953
Labour's lost generation,
when it increased 250 000

1226668290
01:09:01.954 --> 01:09:04.764
the number of nights in their
last few years in office,

1610154647
01:09:04.842 --> 01:09:09.245
