to paragraph 268 of the report.

1930224948
01:09:29.297 --> 01:09:29.496
Mr.

2680492530
01:09:29.498 --> 01:09:33.208
speaker, it says, and I quote,
the UK's Neet crisis is much more long

3948394394
01:09:33.838 --> 01:09:37.840
term and deep seated than any decisions
taken in the last few years.

3832391565
01:09:37.841 --> 01:09:41.188
And at paragraph 266 on Nick
Smith specifically, again,

2435968474
01:09:41.190 --> 01:09:45.447
I quote it is worth remembering
that those under 21 remain exempt

371880730
01:09:45.841 --> 01:09:54.878
from employer NICs and as
the review has already Speaker.

3823630188
01:09:54.879 --> 01:10:03.494
This is their record, their
problem highlighted,

66771877
01:10:03.495 --> 01:10:05.601
the increase in youth inactivity long Mr.

1613921486
01:10:05.602 --> 01:10:07.056
speaker, on that very point.

3637152966
01:10:07.057 --> 01:10:08.641
There was no explanation or.

1787518678
01:10:08.642 --> 01:10:09.042
Please.

866116081
01:10:09.043 --> 01:10:11.149
>> This Urgent Question has been granted.

3346362353
01:10:11.150 --> 01:10:13.860
I don't need the frontbench
to come in and then start

2006136971
01:10:13.861 --> 01:10:16.017
