3113481658
01:10:54.102 --> 01:10:57.146
To how do we help you change your life?

55828017
01:10:57.147 --> 01:10:58.451
That is what matters, Mr.

2517740400
01:10:58.452 --> 01:10:58.902
Speaker.

2629150177
01:10:58.903 --> 01:11:01.260
That is exactly what this
government is doing.

3186873524
01:11:01.261 --> 01:11:03.199
Fixing the broken welfare system that

2883543366
01:11:03.200 --> 01:11:06.644
we inherited from the party opposite.

532913587
01:11:06.645 --> 01:11:08.147
Rebalancing Universal Credit.

1651710153
01:11:08.844 --> 01:11:12.643
Implementing right to try tackling
their backlog on access to work.

1160146096
01:11:12.644 --> 01:11:16.601
And of course, our £2.5 billion
