3437813936
01:12:22.696 --> 01:12:24.543
But is is my my right hon.

2468770118
01:12:24.544 --> 01:12:28.391
Friend is concerned as
as me that we mustn't

2554888496
01:12:28.392 --> 01:12:30.447
