I will make a statement.

3281170455
02:07:46.527 --> 02:07:49.551
>> About the murder of Henry Nowak.

3534123385
02:07:49.552 --> 02:07:50.303
Last December.

1885533314
02:07:50.304 --> 02:07:50.955
Henry, aged.

3817669667
02:07:50.956 --> 02:07:51.407
Just 18.

3727794666
02:07:51.408 --> 02:07:53.012
>> Was a first year university.

862964046
02:07:53.014 --> 02:07:53.866
>> Student with.

720828493
02:07:53.900 --> 02:07:55.205
>> His life ahead of him.

1349622962
02:07:55.206 --> 02:08:00.512
He was kind, hardworking, loved
by his family and friends.

3489857509
02:08:00.514 --> 02:08:06.702
His murder at the hands of Vikram
Vikram Digwa was a horrifying act.

841729643
02:08:06.703 --> 02:08:09.955
Digwa murdered Henry and then
lied about him as he lay dying,

579363153
02:08:09.956 --> 02:08:14.300
falsely accusing him of racism.

320176878
02:08:14.301 --> 02:08:15.305
It was an evil act.

1676404605
02:08:15.306 --> 02:08:17.514
I know the thoughts of
the whole House will

1446279682
02:08:17.515 --> 02:08:20.753
now be with Henry's
family and his friends,

4102323237
02:08:20.753 --> 02:08:23.401
just as mine are, for what they have been

1438638768
02:08:23.402 --> 02:08:27.101
through is heartbreaking for most of us.

2806826831
02:08:27.101 --> 02:08:27.802
Unimaginable.

1410090881
02:08:27.803 --> 02:08:30.860
I know nothing can take
their pain and loss away.

2667632150
02:08:30.862 --> 02:08:34.902
But yesterday we saw
some measure of justice.

3100269871
02:08:34.903 --> 02:08:39.600
Digwa was sentenced to life imprisonment.

1354091304
02:08:39.601 --> 02:08:41.708
He will serve a minimum term of 21 years.

365187870
02:08:41.902 --> 02:08:47.053
His mother, Kirron Kher, has been
convicted of assisting an offender.

1404203064
02:08:47.054 --> 02:08:49.603
She is due to be sentenced
on 17th of July.

3468402765
02:08:49.604 --> 02:08:53.454
And today the Crown Prosecution
Service has authorised further

38865236
02:08:53.455 --> 02:08:58.906
charges against other members
of the attacker's family,

1989502766
02:08:58.907 --> 02:09:01.613
with further sentencing
and possible charges pending.

1003733695
02:09:01.614 --> 02:09:04.475
We must be cautious still in
what we say about this case

1324020867
02:09:06.902 --> 02:09:09.360
so that we do not place
any proceedings at risk.

806489928
02:09:09.985 --> 02:09:12.092
However, I can and must pay tribute today

2166922994
02:09:12.092 --> 02:09:14.311
to the dignified and powerful words

1746633516
02:09:14.312 --> 02:09:17.003
of the Nowak family in the statement they

2993265136
02:09:17.003 --> 02:09:19.500
gave after yesterday's sentencing.

2314809242
02:09:19.501 --> 02:09:20.603
They deserve answers.

1612873326
02:09:20.604 --> 02:09:22.903
They deserve answers in particular about

3295512949
02:09:22.904 --> 02:09:25.202
what happened on that awful night

1200631244
02:09:25.203 --> 02:09:30.161
and the actions of the police
officers who arrived on the scene.

1529980770
02:09:30.162 --> 02:09:34.006
I expect many in this House,
and many more across this country,

3706837908
02:09:34.007 --> 02:09:39.957
have now seen the police officer's
body cam footage released last night.

3220110789
02:09:39.958 --> 02:09:43.154
It is, without question,
a disturbing and tragic thing to see.

531903980
02:09:43.155 --> 02:09:48.355
People are rightly asking questions
about how the situation was handled,

475470543
02:09:48.356 --> 02:09:50.312
and they are shocked and disquieted to

1323517901
02:09:50.313 --> 02:09:54.458
hear Henry's words I can't breathe.

4050659478
02:09:54.458 --> 02:09:58.011
I know that it is difficult to
wait any longer for answers,

2267579736
02:09:58.012 --> 02:10:00.420
but there is a proper
process to assess whether

3547260609
02:10:01.856 --> 02:10:04.262
there have been incidents
of police misconduct,

3533460035
02:10:04.262 --> 02:10:07.271
led by the Independent Office
for Police Conduct, the IOPC.

872387423
02:10:07.273 --> 02:10:11.303
They will determine what could
and should have been done differently.

1517353744
02:10:11.304 --> 02:10:13.706
They will determine what action may need

1952699115
02:10:13.707 --> 02:10:17.418
to be taken against individual officers.

4214489461
02:10:17.419 --> 02:10:20.253
The family yesterday
called on me and I quote,

4028932986
02:10:20.255 --> 02:10:22.161
to ensure the IOPC has the resources,

1123466180
02:10:23.905 --> 02:10:26.663
authority and independence
it needs to conduct a full,

3955526169
02:10:26.904 --> 02:10:28.907
fearless and transparent investigation.

3975654475
02:10:28.908 --> 02:10:29.108
Mr.

3576493624
02:10:30.860 --> 02:10:33.622
speaker, I can confirm to you
today that I will do so.

2525865795
02:10:33.904 --> 02:10:36.362
The Iopc will be equipped
and encouraged to act,

2033330543
02:10:36.904 --> 02:10:38.560
to find the truth and to ensure,

918491975
02:10:38.561 --> 02:10:42.357
if necessary, that there are consequences.

4162833753
02:10:42.358 --> 02:10:46.056
There have been accusations,
I know, of two tier policing,

3716183601
02:10:46.057 --> 02:10:50.360
that one community has been
prioritised over another.

2158219972
02:10:50.360 --> 02:10:52.217
It will be for the Iopc to determine

6231579
02:10:52.219 --> 02:10:55.408
the facts with regard
to this specific case,

1115733588
02:10:55.409 --> 02:10:58.208
and I cannot and will not comment on them.

1803118636
02:10:58.208 --> 02:11:00.462
But let me say this on the question of

165428205
02:11:00.463 --> 02:11:02.266
preferential treatment more widely,

3618511579
02:11:03.904 --> 02:11:05.961
the police in this country have a sacred

75022422
02:11:05.962 --> 02:11:09.461
duty to police without fear or favour.

4105478151
02:11:09.462 --> 02:11:13.560
Everyone in this country
is equal before the law.

2783983642
02:11:13.561 --> 02:11:17.462
It is the promise upon which our
whole justice system rests,

741353578
02:11:17.463 --> 02:11:20.511
and the quality of every citizen is

4041947984
02:11:20.512 --> 02:11:23.057
the foundation on which the openness,

4053001523
02:11:23.058 --> 02:11:26.907
tolerance and generosity
of this country rests.

4009692225
02:11:26.908 --> 02:11:31.050
Let me also be clear about one other
thing a dangerous undercurrent

1352002269
02:11:31.051 --> 02:11:33.969
that I have seen in
the reaction to this awful crime.

2565943641
02:11:34.905 --> 02:11:40.605
Threats against police officers
are utterly unacceptable.

574416971
02:11:40.606 --> 02:11:43.012
There can be no justification
for intimidation,

262131812
02:11:43.012 --> 02:11:46.255
abuse or attempts to take
the law into one's own hands.

4096201169
02:11:46.256 --> 02:11:50.057
A police officer unrelated to
this case has been misidentified

3269851486
02:11:50.058 --> 02:11:52.655
online and subjected to death threats.

3733654969
02:11:52.656 --> 02:11:57.508
He has been forced to relocate to
protect himself and his family.

1574814130
02:11:57.509 --> 02:12:00.063
Misinformation and inflammatory commentary

4282660706
02:12:00.064 --> 02:12:05.007
is making a dreadful situation even worse.

3512503052
02:12:05.008 --> 02:12:07.757
We must all >> Together, condemn it, and.

2195583281
02:12:07.758 --> 02:12:10.267
We must also allow
the facts to be established to

304507827
02:12:10.268 --> 02:12:13.305
the appropriate investigations
and the courts.

2115683654
02:12:13.306 --> 02:12:15.413
And we must do so calmly and responsibly.

3291575219
02:12:17.907 --> 02:12:20.163
The Nowak family
and Henry's memory deserve.

1120442541
02:12:20.164 --> 02:12:23.063
They have also called on
us all to take action.

2136739706
02:12:23.904 --> 02:12:27.756
Action to address the daily tragedy
of knife crime in this country.

934946525
02:12:27.757 --> 02:12:31.668
This government is committed to
halving knife crime in this decade.

1901185248
02:12:31.669 --> 02:12:34.628
Since the start of this Parliament,
we have made progress.

2290975186
02:12:35.905 --> 02:12:37.460
Knife crime has fallen by 10%.

3050463695
02:12:37.461 --> 02:12:43.116
Knife homicides are down 27% at
their lowest level in a decade.

59287211
02:12:43.117 --> 02:12:44.622
But clearly, we must do more.

2547838665
02:12:44.623 --> 02:12:48.213
Whilst there are still tragedies
like this one, and for that reason,

2862032897
02:12:48.214 --> 02:12:51.612
we have recently published our
Halving Knife crime plan.

1962684303
02:12:51.905 --> 02:12:54.114
It sets out how we will
go further to drive

361980810
02:12:54.905 --> 02:12:56.608
sustained reductions in violence.

2115731862
02:12:56.609 --> 02:13:00.164
It brings together action
across government and across

3860463710
02:13:00.165 --> 02:13:02.773
society to stop people from
turning to knife crime,

1005389745
02:13:02.774 --> 02:13:07.501
and to ensure that perpetrators are
caught and brought to justice.

4116178623
02:13:07.502 --> 02:13:10.105
Amongst a range of measures, this will see

1218012367
02:13:10.106 --> 02:13:12.211
schools and families supported to address

2031212665
02:13:12.212 --> 02:13:14.168
the root causes of knife crime through

1059494821
02:13:14.169 --> 02:13:17.915
the establishment of
50 young futures hubs.

3147203649
02:13:17.916 --> 02:13:20.057
Police using new crime mapping tools to

3506835037
02:13:20.058 --> 02:13:21.811
target enforcement more precisely,

3623877569
02:13:21.812 --> 02:13:26.258
and making better use of stop
and search and cruel and exploitative

3830088010
02:13:26.259 --> 02:13:29.065
drug gangs stopped from
criminally exploiting children,

3967114525
02:13:29.065 --> 02:13:33.250
preventing the knife violence that
is driven by the county lines trade.

2923280019
02:13:33.251 --> 02:13:36.904
In relation to knife controls,
there have been calls to limit

367707983
02:13:36.905 --> 02:13:40.106
the right of Sikhs to carry
their ceremonial knife.

611027871
02:13:40.107 --> 02:13:43.258
The kirpan, one of the five
holy items in their faith,

3666116280
02:13:43.259 --> 02:13:47.862
the Offensive Weapons Act of 2019,
passed under the previous government,

4250099543
02:13:47.908 --> 02:13:50.012
clarified and strengthened existing legal

751167622
02:13:50.909 --> 02:13:52.964
protections in relation to long kirpans.

4042817191
02:13:52.965 --> 02:13:55.258
This included extending defences so that

2902678462
02:13:55.259 --> 02:13:57.855
kirpans can be lawfully possessed

2540484553
02:13:57.856 --> 02:14:02.613
for religious reasons and used in
religious and ceremonial contexts.

2195088031
02:14:02.614 --> 02:14:06.864
But let me be clear carrying
a knife for the purpose

2220898395
02:14:06.865 --> 02:14:09.161
of religious observance is one thing.

4125512220
02:14:09.162 --> 02:14:13.467
Using it as so tragically occurred
in this case is quite another.

1908792401
02:14:13.469 --> 02:14:17.265
It is a vile act, a crime
of the utmost severity,

50708448
02:14:19.910 --> 02:14:22.368
and it will be met with
the severest punishment.

324733455
02:14:22.369 --> 02:14:24.875
Yesterday, the Nowak family
ended their statement

1812249645
02:14:24.876 --> 02:14:27.262
with a powerful call to us all.

2184404389
02:14:27.264 --> 02:14:34.410
I quote, we do not want his death to
be used to create further division,

836577140
02:14:34.411 --> 02:14:35.363
hatred or tension.

2818412551
02:14:35.364 --> 02:14:38.926
They quoted the words of the prosecuting
lawyer and I quote again, Mr.

3616212154
02:14:38.927 --> 02:14:41.083
Speaker, this is not a case about Sikhism.

2857797014
02:14:41.085 --> 02:14:43.163
This is not a case about racism.

2558166869
02:14:43.164 --> 02:14:46.309
This is a case about murder.

1630083615
02:14:46.310 --> 02:14:47.313
I echo those words.

1835817958
02:14:47.314 --> 02:14:52.312
We cannot allow this murder to turn
communities against one another.

2442744919
02:14:52.313 --> 02:14:57.605
We must condemn those who seek personal
political profit from tragedy.

1696103119
02:14:57.606 --> 02:15:01.274
Instead, we must show who we
really are in this country.

3968609669
02:15:01.275 --> 02:15:04.857
This was a murder,
a vile and violent crime.

2256674682
02:15:04.858 --> 02:15:07.860
The punishment must be reserved for those

4243968218
02:15:07.860 --> 02:15:09.516
who are responsible for the act.

557049393
02:15:09.517 --> 02:15:13.354
We do not believe in collective
punishment in this country.

3088119216
02:15:13.355 --> 02:15:16.458
Instead, we stand together
against an act of pure evil.

375509641
02:15:16.460 --> 02:15:19.911
We condemn those who committed
this heinous crime.

3871495904
02:15:19.912 --> 02:15:24.211
Not all those who share their
faith or their ethnicity.

2453380508
02:15:24.212 --> 02:15:28.211
Yesterday, a sentence was
handed down in court.

1163874772
02:15:28.212 --> 02:15:30.270
I know it will never be enough.

2337286037
02:15:30.271 --> 02:15:34.262
The loss felt by Henry Nowak family
and friends will last forever.

3196310503
02:15:34.262 --> 02:15:37.520
A wonderful young man will
never enjoy the promise

603326671
02:15:37.521 --> 02:15:40.216
of the life that stretched out before him.

507086654
02:15:40.217 --> 02:15:44.211
The evil acts of his murderer
and accomplice will never be undone.

297181794
02:15:44.212 --> 02:15:48.309
But we can choose to use this
moment to pursue positive change.

1207000186
02:15:48.310 --> 02:15:50.368
We are still limited in what we can say.

3761900906
02:15:50.909 --> 02:15:55.308
There is a sentence to be handed
down and further charges may follow.

1972969685
02:15:55.309 --> 02:15:59.060
And there is an IOPC
investigation ongoing.

4134988863
02:15:59.061 --> 02:16:02.172
But I call on everyone here to
be responsible in this moment,

2589963385
02:16:02.173 --> 02:16:04.230
to allow justice to run its full course.

4221899669
02:16:04.231 --> 02:16:07.311
But while we must be limited
in what we can say,

1600684665
02:16:07.312 --> 02:16:10.507
we must not be limited in how we act.

2026517354
02:16:10.508 --> 02:16:14.107
I will end with the words of
the Nowak family once more.

1144641524
02:16:14.108 --> 02:16:17.615
Last night they wrote that no
other family should experience

1470513403
02:16:17.616 --> 02:16:22.164
the heartbreak and horror of
losing a child to knife crime.

765208815
02:16:22.910 --> 02:16:27.260
Let that be the challenge to
us all across this house,

1268904788
02:16:27.261 --> 02:16:29.165
across government and across society.

1462164716
02:16:29.166 --> 02:16:32.580
It is the very least we can do to
honour the memory of Henry Nowak.

3798016774
02:16:32.581 --> 02:16:32.781
Mr.

441675881
02:16:32.782 --> 02:16:35.189
speaker, I commend this
statement to the House.

1346221622
02:16:35.190 --> 02:16:38.458
>> Chris Philp Shadow Home Secretary.

18550161
02:16:38.460 --> 02:16:39.162
>> Thank you.

2935375644
02:16:39.163 --> 02:16:39.514
>> Mr.

1298794115
02:16:39.515 --> 02:16:39.965
Speaker.

2292997141
02:16:39.966 --> 02:16:41.369
I thank the Home Secretary.

2831358128
02:16:41.371 --> 02:16:42.324
And thank you, Mr.

3408792525
02:16:42.324 --> 02:16:45.434
Speaker, for ensuring
the government came to the House today.

1066761878
02:16:47.913 --> 02:16:52.505
The murder of Henry Nowak is
devastating for his family.

35189064
02:16:52.506 --> 02:16:56.109
He was an innocent young man on the way

1329233704
02:16:56.110 --> 02:16:57.815
home when he was brutally killed.

4281275029
02:16:57.815 --> 02:17:02.026
Henry's family have suffered
an unimaginable loss,

3835958995
02:17:02.027 --> 02:17:07.414
and I know the thoughts of
the whole house will be with them all.

3896301006
02:17:07.415 --> 02:17:13.011
The evil murderer Vickrum Digwa
lied from start to finish,

671610894
02:17:13.012 --> 02:17:16.456
including a false allegation of racism.

4125973848
02:17:16.457 --> 02:17:17.962
But on arriving at the scene,

3916343373
02:17:17.963 --> 02:17:21.966
the police appeared more concerned
with the accusation of racism

1428302975
02:17:21.967 --> 02:17:26.106
and even the possibility
that Digwa himself was

1268103542
02:17:26.107 --> 02:17:28.163
injured than they were in helping Henry.

1652838655
02:17:29.867 --> 02:17:34.264
Henry told the police he could
not breathe nine times.

3208543796
02:17:34.265 --> 02:17:37.273
He told them he had been
stabbed four times.

3112249555
02:17:37.274 --> 02:17:41.507
The response from the officer
we've all heard was to say,

3912534946
02:17:41.508 --> 02:17:42.963
I don't think you have made.

973228170
02:17:42.964 --> 02:17:47.467
Henry was handcuffed and dragged
across the ground as he lay dying.

1633092652
02:17:47.469 --> 02:17:52.168
Can you imagine what he must have
felt as he cried out for help

3258718523
02:17:52.169 --> 02:17:55.517
and was ignored as the officers
who should have worked

2354765056
02:17:55.518 --> 02:18:00.018
to save him instead handcuffed
him and inquired after

2988337684
02:18:00.019 --> 02:18:05.925
the welfare of his killer
standing just inches away.

2395179150
02:18:05.926 --> 02:18:09.015
Henry's dad, Mark, said this.

423221237
02:18:09.016 --> 02:18:12.362
Henry did not die with dignity.

3822382042
02:18:12.363 --> 02:18:14.471
He did not die with the care he deserved.

2957095030
02:18:14.472 --> 02:18:18.267
He lost consciousness
before anyone believed him.

1965835326
02:18:21.916 --> 02:18:24.613
So we need the IOPC to
urgently and transparently

1839907087
02:18:24.614 --> 02:18:25.818
report into how it was.

1899653030
02:18:25.819 --> 02:18:28.877
The police attending were more
concerned with the accusation

4003467769
02:18:28.878 --> 02:18:32.576
of racism than they were
in helping a dying man.

24866407
02:18:32.577 --> 02:18:32.777
Mr.

2565092382
02:18:32.778 --> 02:18:36.068
speaker, we cannot tolerate
a situation where false

4262901286
02:18:37.912 --> 02:18:40.368
allegations of racism by
criminals are believed.

750558574
02:18:40.369 --> 02:18:45.613
We cannot allow the colour of
someone's skin to be a consideration

2633901685
02:18:45.614 --> 02:18:50.064
in how the police or other
public services treat people.

141247419
02:18:50.065 --> 02:18:51.419
And yet this has happened.

3395777820
02:18:51.420 --> 02:18:53.776
Just recently, we learned
that Valdo Kalakani,

3449367973
02:18:54.912 --> 02:18:56.967
who murdered three people in Nottingham,

2782343957
02:18:56.967 --> 02:18:59.424
was not sectioned by mental
health professionals

1388357051
02:18:59.425 --> 02:19:02.070
because they thought there was,

2677760202
02:19:02.071 --> 02:19:06.314
and I quote,
an overrepresentation of young

2884916102
02:19:06.315 --> 02:19:08.467
black males in mental health detention.

627653153
02:19:08.467 --> 02:19:12.413
The consequent failure to
section Valdo Kalakani,

3123030074
02:19:12.414 --> 02:19:13.919
in part because he was black,

1882279784
02:19:13.920 --> 02:19:18.374
led directly to the murder
of three innocent people.

1229865198
02:19:18.375 --> 02:19:22.818
The headteacher of Axl Cabana was accused

3713704797
02:19:22.819 --> 02:19:24.924
of racist stereotyping when she described

3470361636
02:19:24.925 --> 02:19:26.881
Redditch Cabana as a threat to safety,

2372515154
02:19:26.882 --> 02:19:29.572
and the risk assessment was watered down.

780374936
02:19:29.573 --> 02:19:33.710
Redcar Cabana, of course,
went on to stab and murder

1841485488
02:19:33.711 --> 02:19:37.064
three young girls at
a Southport dance class.

1193915733
02:19:37.065 --> 02:19:37.516
But, Mr.

1595667610
02:19:37.517 --> 02:19:40.011
Speaker, this has not
happened by accident.

3874787264
02:19:40.012 --> 02:19:44.018
It is enshrined in
the police's own policy documents.

4170213289
02:19:44.019 --> 02:19:48.508
The police anti-racism commitment,

829882701
02:19:48.509 --> 02:19:52.166
published in March 2025 by
the Npcc and the College of Policing,

334666499
02:19:52.167 --> 02:19:54.172
urges police forces to reverse engineer

995858368
02:19:54.173 --> 02:19:56.429
the same arrest rates
between ethnic groups,

2678262808
02:19:56.430 --> 02:19:58.786
even though the offending
rates are different.

1376760741
02:19:58.787 --> 02:20:02.521
By treating different
ethnic groups differently.

2876897357
02:20:02.521 --> 02:20:04.078
Let that sink in for a moment.

2491924082
02:20:04.079 --> 02:20:09.062
An official police document
actually says people should be

1415126194
02:20:09.063 --> 02:20:11.821
treated differently based on
the colour of their skin.

1098599808
02:20:11.822 --> 02:20:14.212
I've said before at this
Dispatch Box at least

415754740
02:20:14.213 --> 02:20:16.268
twice that document should be withdrawn.

1682503232
02:20:16.917 --> 02:20:19.372
The dangerous ideology of
so-called anti-racism,

1169353641
02:20:19.909 --> 02:20:24.664
allowing people to be treated
differently based on race must end.

2703955906
02:20:24.665 --> 02:20:27.713
Extreme activists have
the policy making process,

4155852535
02:20:27.714 --> 02:20:29.220
and this is where it has led.

2596734730
02:20:29.221 --> 02:20:30.979
It has no place in policing.

2476175099
02:20:30.980 --> 02:20:32.284
It has no place anywhere.

3700248583
02:20:32.914 --> 02:20:36.766
So does the Home Secretary agree
that the so-called police

883515770
02:20:36.767 --> 02:20:40.617
anti-racism commitment must
urgently be withdrawn?

1836934060
02:20:40.618 --> 02:20:43.866
It is morally wrong
and it is dangerous as well.

2070729006
02:20:43.867 --> 02:20:47.863
Police forces must focus
on catching criminals

3704311632
02:20:47.864 --> 02:20:49.318
and keeping the public safe.

2636570147
02:20:49.319 --> 02:20:53.917
They must simply treat
everyone exactly the same.

4136537511
02:20:53.918 --> 02:20:57.068
I want to finish with Mark
Nowak words yesterday.

4111165329
02:20:57.069 --> 02:21:01.271
Henry's father.

2685201204
02:21:01.273 --> 02:21:01.975
He said this.

1620480706
02:21:01.976 --> 02:21:02.678
Henry was 18.

131343333
02:21:02.679 --> 02:21:06.871
He was kind, ambitious,
loved, and full of promise.

3405387013
02:21:06.872 --> 02:21:13.764
He had his whole life ahead of him,
but that future was stolen from him.

1309618608
02:21:13.765 --> 02:21:18.119
And no verdict and no sentence
will ever give it back.

4158516786
02:21:18.121 --> 02:21:18.321
Mr.

3455936802
02:21:18.322 --> 02:21:21.081
speaker, it is true that
nothing can bring Henry back.

3910022202
02:21:21.082 --> 02:21:25.173
But let us make sure that no
one ever again experiences

1968299177
02:21:28.873 --> 02:21:31.030
what Henry did in his last tragic moments.

3076731233
02:21:31.031 --> 02:21:32.686
>> Home Secretary thank you, Mr.

3618233200
02:21:32.687 --> 02:21:33.137
Speaker.

56880859
02:21:33.137 --> 02:21:37.821
Let me thank the shadow Home
Secretary for his remarks

2675391766
02:21:37.822 --> 02:21:40.622
and for the tone in which he reflected on

2430574664
02:21:40.623 --> 02:21:43.723
the this horrific murder
and the words of the family,

614464129
02:21:43.724 --> 02:21:46.722
which obviously he knows I share as well.

591843051
02:21:46.723 --> 02:21:48.864
Let me just say his his initial point.

2210396111
02:21:48.865 --> 02:21:51.118
I would normally let it slide, Mr.

3998434859
02:21:51.119 --> 02:21:54.428
Speaker, but I think there's far
too much misinformation floating

1814479971
02:21:54.429 --> 02:21:57.773
around social media for me to
just leave this one unchallenged.

3687055516
02:21:57.774 --> 02:22:00.634
On the government coming to
the House, he will know that

2120451830
02:22:00.635 --> 02:22:03.681
the proceedings and sentencing
concluded at 4:00 yesterday.

956540393
02:22:03.682 --> 02:22:06.089
We said we would come
immediately thereafter to

3509779376
02:22:06.090 --> 02:22:08.798
the House and we have presented
ourselves here today.

2122344385
02:22:08.799 --> 02:22:11.056
We have responded in
an appropriate way with

2908284601
02:22:11.057 --> 02:22:14.113
all of the facts that are disposal and all

1303525767
02:22:14.114 --> 02:22:16.271
of the judge's remarks at our disposal for

4011572850
02:22:16.271 --> 02:22:18.278
our review before coming to this House.

1910988842
02:22:18.279 --> 02:22:20.436
And I think it's important that we respond

3862197821
02:22:20.437 --> 02:22:22.243
in these moments in a measured way.

4074578852
02:22:22.244 --> 02:22:25.471
And that is what we,
the government, have sought to do.

3170707342
02:22:25.472 --> 02:22:28.922
He referred to evidence in relation
to the Valdo Calocane inquiry.

3878152747
02:22:28.923 --> 02:22:31.479
He will know that the inquiry into

3215692587
02:22:31.480 --> 02:22:35.224
the Nottingham attacks is well underway,

2351384777
02:22:35.225 --> 02:22:38.637
and I don't think it would be
appropriate for me from this Dispatch

27516342
02:22:38.637 --> 02:22:41.547
Box to pre-empt any findings
that the inquiry might make.

1269738969
02:22:41.917 --> 02:22:45.774
But of course, all of
the actions and assumptions made

1832101120
02:22:45.775 --> 02:22:48.130
by professionals of
different public services,

4227477689
02:22:48.131 --> 02:22:50.387
including the police
and the health service,

949773949
02:22:50.917 --> 02:22:53.173
are subject to scrutiny
within that inquiry.

2209443284
02:22:53.174 --> 02:22:55.722
I'm sure those are matters that we will

2325119497
02:22:55.723 --> 02:22:59.119
return to as as that inquiry report.

1863544132
02:22:59.121 --> 02:23:02.132
He did refer to
the findings of phase one of

2466750858
02:23:02.133 --> 02:23:06.270
the Southport inquiry in
relation to those horrific

506583246
02:23:06.271 --> 02:23:08.866
murders and the findings
in relation to how

3154198124
02:23:08.867 --> 02:23:12.467
the public service systems, in that case,

565814372
02:23:12.469 --> 02:23:14.375
in relation to acts of Cabana centred

2043323243
02:23:14.376 --> 02:23:16.382
the danger he might have posed himself,

4274584106
02:23:16.383 --> 02:23:19.433
given his mental health
diagnosis and did not take into

1472730274
02:23:20.913 --> 02:23:23.470
account the danger he posed
potentially to others.

3165097422
02:23:23.471 --> 02:23:25.726
There have been
recommendations he will know

11565702
02:23:25.728 --> 02:23:27.985
that have been made for
change in this area,

3058020768
02:23:28.876 --> 02:23:31.785
which the government will
respond to fully in due course.

1437294945
02:23:31.786 --> 02:23:35.517
But let me be very clear
with him and all members

1326994141
02:23:35.518 --> 02:23:37.274
in this House in all such matters,

1935755878
02:23:37.275 --> 02:23:39.383
in terms of how we engage with our public

2394351341
02:23:39.384 --> 02:23:42.220
services and how they assist risk.

1785946850
02:23:42.221 --> 02:23:45.922
The only important factor is
the risk an individual poses.

1188569409
02:23:45.923 --> 02:23:49.172
Not their race, not their religion,
or indeed anything else.

852767324
02:23:49.921 --> 02:23:52.378
And we will not tolerate
a situation where other

4102542168
02:23:52.916 --> 02:23:55.071
irrelevant factors are taken into account.

3362884149
02:23:55.072 --> 02:23:57.771
I repeat again, all are
equal before the law,

1211929800
02:23:57.771 --> 02:24:02.034
and every public service
needs to bear that in mind.

442343221
02:24:02.035 --> 02:24:05.271
He he referred to the police
anti-racism commitment.

2034046842
02:24:05.919 --> 02:24:09.715
He will obviously remember, I'm
sure that the race action plan for

2329599709
02:24:09.716 --> 02:24:13.024
the police began life under
the previous conservative government.

3384185722
02:24:13.025 --> 02:24:17.278
In fact, I'm old enough to remember
when Theresa May called out

1652358356
02:24:17.921 --> 02:24:21.567
disproportionate use of stop
and search for black communities.

881241988
02:24:21.568 --> 02:24:24.368
In particular, he will
know that the way that

2730997623
02:24:24.369 --> 02:24:26.676
policing works in this
country is by consent.

1986343627
02:24:26.677 --> 02:24:29.980
It is important that the police
retain the confidence of all

784382416
02:24:29.981 --> 02:24:33.324
of the communities that they
police, and that there has.

468579369
02:24:33.326 --> 02:24:35.784
I think he would acknowledge
being a history and

1683576610
02:24:35.785 --> 02:24:39.676
a context here relating
to racism and the police.

4088918809
02:24:39.677 --> 02:24:42.425
Whatever changes are made
that it is important

2912120027
02:24:42.426 --> 02:24:46.073
that nobody overcorrects or course

638859483
02:24:46.074 --> 02:24:48.369
corrects such that all of us as citizens

953382628
02:24:48.371 --> 02:24:50.177
are no longer equal before the law,

3516636391
02:24:50.178 --> 02:24:54.470
and this government will always
ensure that in fulfilling

3915312172
02:24:54.471 --> 02:24:56.978
their sacred duties to
keep our communities safe,

1725260603
02:24:56.979 --> 02:24:59.637
that the police always act
without fear and fervour,

1766938550
02:24:59.637 --> 02:25:03.320
and always ensure that every
citizen is treated equally.

315347302
02:25:03.321 --> 02:25:09.975
But I'm sure he wouldn't
want to do down or ignore

1657915905
02:25:09.976 --> 02:25:13.474
a historic and legitimate
concerns that there

449318133
02:25:13.475 --> 02:25:18.923
have been from some communities
about institutional racism,

380573134
02:25:18.924 --> 02:25:20.678
as well as differential treatment.

3913959810
02:25:20.679 --> 02:25:22.572
I condemn all types of differential

4279333694
02:25:22.573 --> 02:25:24.678
and every type of differential treatment.

3448734234
02:25:24.679 --> 02:25:25.966
I do not stand for it.

3942813364
02:25:25.967 --> 02:25:29.228
My own track record as a government
Minister shows I will always

1282494906
02:25:29.229 --> 02:25:32.132
act when there is evidence
of differential treatment,

2144638984
02:25:32.133 --> 02:25:34.842
and it is absolutely vital
that that message is heard

3037990916
02:25:35.920 --> 02:25:38.328
loud and clear across
the whole of our country.

2226099444
02:25:38.329 --> 02:25:39.934
>> Darren Paffey thank you, Mr.

3962980058
02:25:39.935 --> 02:25:40.385
Speaker.

4196696123
02:25:40.386 --> 02:25:44.470
>> And can I thank the Secretary
of State for her statement?

1078403861
02:25:44.471 --> 02:25:46.628
Henry was a popular and much loved student

3842150574
02:25:46.628 --> 02:25:48.474
at the University of Southampton,

1154017323
02:25:48.475 --> 02:25:50.924
and his murder has horrified our city.

4102133292
02:25:50.925 --> 02:25:51.929
I know both my hon.

2063686592
02:25:51.930 --> 02:25:53.935
Friend the Member for Southampton Test,

1726692533
02:25:53.936 --> 02:25:56.394
and I want to commend
everyone at the University

2729224948
02:25:56.395 --> 02:25:58.902
for their response
and support for the university

3893793102
02:25:58.903 --> 02:26:00.619
community following this tragedy.

1088668257
02:26:00.619 --> 02:26:00.820
Mr.

2659577794
02:26:00.821 --> 02:26:04.374
speaker, like many, I've
watched the body cam footage

665187289
02:26:04.375 --> 02:26:07.467
and it is both heartbreaking
and infuriating.

3652324699
02:26:07.469 --> 02:26:11.072
It makes it plain for all
to see how Henry posed

3833836758
02:26:11.073 --> 02:26:13.429
no threat that would
warrant being handcuffed,

1039540601
02:26:13.430 --> 02:26:17.128
and yet was treated as a criminal
based on the lies of his murderer.

1494851514
02:26:17.128 --> 02:26:20.228
Now, no one in their right
mind thinks that one Sikh,

1351928206
02:26:20.229 --> 02:26:22.286
or 1 or 2 police officers represents all

3090479650
02:26:22.287 --> 02:26:24.320
Sikhs or the entire police force.

234738079
02:26:24.321 --> 02:26:26.829
As Henry's father has said,
this is about murder,

557266857
02:26:26.830 --> 02:26:30.686
about our response to it,
and about our prevention of it.

2725017249
02:26:30.687 --> 02:26:33.525
So I have two questions for my right hon.

4054533498
02:26:33.526 --> 02:26:33.926
Friend.

961777149
02:26:33.927 --> 02:26:36.470
We have a knife problem in this country.

3296117727
02:26:36.471 --> 02:26:38.929
That's why we've taken
early steps to ban zombie

656469095
02:26:38.930 --> 02:26:41.087
knives and to crack down on knife sellers.

2819384797
02:26:41.088 --> 02:26:44.301
But it is obvious that is not
enough and we have to go further.

4287356860
02:26:44.302 --> 02:26:46.574
So will the Secretary of State commit to

3368602574
02:26:46.576 --> 02:26:49.972
clarifying a set of tough and consistent

2877564443
02:26:49.973 --> 02:26:52.974
knife laws and the resources to enforce

2849374324
02:26:52.975 --> 02:26:54.882
them so that we can actually move on?

1055185839
02:26:54.923 --> 02:26:58.975
And secondly, I echo the words of
Henry's dad as she did and asked

1286196552
02:26:58.976 --> 02:27:01.668
the Secretary of State to guarantee that

519173986
02:27:01.669 --> 02:27:03.374
the IOPC will have the resources,

766308557
02:27:03.375 --> 02:27:07.723
the authority and the independence
it needs to conduct a full,

759796378
02:27:07.724 --> 02:27:09.726
fearless and transparent investigation.

3671349563
02:27:10.916 --> 02:27:14.225
Will she guarantee that because
the catastrophic errors that were

455201866
02:27:14.226 --> 02:27:19.626
made when police officers got to
Henry must never happen again?

736504520
02:27:19.627 --> 02:27:22.773
>> Well, let me thank my hon.

223452611
02:27:22.774 --> 02:27:25.331
Friend for his contribution
and for his questions.

4168909351
02:27:25.332 --> 02:27:26.937
Let me give him that guarantee.

1187321436
02:27:27.923 --> 02:27:31.128
The IOPC will and do have
the resources that they

1047258158
02:27:31.130 --> 02:27:33.436
need in order to conduct
their investigation,

3471981821
02:27:33.922 --> 02:27:36.081
and I know that they will do so, you know,

40043821
02:27:36.082 --> 02:27:42.677
with the full independence that is
afforded to them in our system.

2853058779
02:27:42.678 --> 02:27:45.271
I understand that they intend to report

2056486423
02:27:45.271 --> 02:27:47.177
finally within the next three months.

2164370636
02:27:47.178 --> 02:27:51.087
And I do believe that a meeting is
now taking place with the family.

850635764
02:27:51.088 --> 02:27:52.842
Some contact had been made before,

2329036595
02:27:52.844 --> 02:27:56.270
but they were waiting for
the end of the criminal trial.

954596642
02:27:56.271 --> 02:27:57.475
So of course they will.

2492869066
02:27:57.476 --> 02:27:58.680
They will do their job.

2174150270
02:27:58.681 --> 02:28:00.788
They are getting on with doing their job,

901902102
02:28:00.789 --> 02:28:03.398
and I expect them to report
as quickly as possible.

2552506793
02:28:03.399 --> 02:28:05.808
But I can give him
the guarantee that he seeks.

2843229702
02:28:05.809 --> 02:28:09.171
He is right about us having a knife
crime problem in this country.

3589702825
02:28:09.172 --> 02:28:11.921
That is why the government
has a landmark commitment

3928180443
02:28:11.922 --> 02:28:14.328
to halving knife crime over a decade.

1378046257
02:28:14.329 --> 02:28:16.987
It's why we've launched
the Knife Crime Action Plan.

214772108
02:28:16.988 --> 02:28:19.597
And let me reassure him,
it does have the resources

3252048243
02:28:19.598 --> 02:28:22.106
it needs in order to fulfil
its historic mission.

245605867
02:28:22.107 --> 02:28:24.512
>> Max Wilkinson Liberal
Democrat spokesperson.

3794906733
02:28:24.512 --> 02:28:25.416
>> Thank you, Mr.

1241468268
02:28:25.417 --> 02:28:25.867
Speaker.

1574800036
02:28:25.868 --> 02:28:29.615
This is a heartbreaking case of
a young man who should be alive today

944038887
02:28:29.616 --> 02:28:32.728
with a happy life ahead of him
because of the forces of evil.

603424663
02:28:32.729 --> 02:28:33.281
He is not.

2142004978
02:28:33.282 --> 02:28:35.440
On behalf of my party, I want to extend my

2286934001
02:28:35.442 --> 02:28:37.547
sympathies to Henry's family and friends,

2291112200
02:28:37.548 --> 02:28:40.623
and I welcome the Home
Secretary's statement today.

1714385043
02:28:40.624 --> 02:28:42.878
The independent investigation
should uncover

2687730909
02:28:42.878 --> 02:28:45.036
how one evil individual was not picked up,

1688247807
02:28:45.037 --> 02:28:48.695
despite apparently exhibiting disturbing
behaviours that saw him ejected

1581679315
02:28:48.696 --> 02:28:53.371
from his place of worship
and having an obsession with weapons.

1782279403
02:28:53.372 --> 02:28:55.226
Police officers, of course, we know,

3153606446
02:28:55.228 --> 02:28:58.732
work under high stress and must
make split second decisions.

3811799432
02:28:58.733 --> 02:29:00.890
We rely on their good judgement every day.

2408526068
02:29:00.924 --> 02:29:02.226
Tragically, in this case,

2602874481
02:29:02.228 --> 02:29:05.332
the officers made a clear
and terrible mistake,

1917314956
02:29:05.333 --> 02:29:08.981
one that failed Henry and has
broken the hearts of his family.

3290207179
02:29:08.982 --> 02:29:11.487
The investigation must
ensure recommendations are

1928514169
02:29:11.488 --> 02:29:13.726
made so nothing like
this can happen again.

375923449
02:29:13.726 --> 02:29:16.938
But as the Home Secretary said,
there must be no doubt, though,

142699789
02:29:16.939 --> 02:29:19.146
that the police officers
that we see on our

729653221
02:29:19.148 --> 02:29:21.053
streets must be treated with respect.

3784051138
02:29:21.054 --> 02:29:23.010
Before going any further, we must also

2745396835
02:29:23.011 --> 02:29:24.815
acknowledge that Digwa betrayed his

2001550288
02:29:24.815 --> 02:29:29.327
faith and he betrayed his community,
and he deserves his punishment.

1537120225
02:29:29.328 --> 02:29:31.735
Regardless of that, it
is incumbent upon all of

963468506
02:29:31.737 --> 02:29:34.077
us in this House when
we discuss this issue,

4162620604
02:29:34.078 --> 02:29:36.336
to bear in mind the words
of Henry's father,

2732378209
02:29:36.337 --> 02:29:38.976
Mark, who said, we do not
want Henry's murder to be

799981429
02:29:38.978 --> 02:29:41.585
used to create further
hatred, division or tension.

494810
02:29:41.586 --> 02:29:44.378
Since the sentencing and
the release of the harrowing

1871218885
02:29:44.378 --> 02:29:46.925
video showing the sickening incident,

339567887
02:29:46.926 --> 02:29:49.332
the vast majority of
politicians have responded

2917806736
02:29:49.333 --> 02:29:51.188
to this matter with due sensitivity,

1893870915
02:29:51.189 --> 02:29:53.095
and that reflects well on this House.

2011768721
02:29:53.096 --> 02:29:56.458
It is therefore all the more
disturbing that we have seen the hon.

3027133761
02:29:56.458 --> 02:29:58.665
Member for Clacton once
again using tragedy

2850822793
02:29:59.924 --> 02:30:01.476
to divide British communities.

2203114453
02:30:01.478 --> 02:30:03.827
We all know why he does this.

2405521412
02:30:03.828 --> 02:30:07.378
He's made a career out of this
and has become rich as a result.

678957168
02:30:07.380 --> 02:30:11.532
But we are also well aware as he
is, that his actions are divisive,

284139765
02:30:11.925 --> 02:30:13.928
dangerous and fundamentally un-british.

3238433472
02:30:13.929 --> 02:30:17.240
The rights of British people to
observe their faith are hard won.

2532461303
02:30:17.241 --> 02:30:22.578
They cannot be contingent upon
the colour of any individual's skin.

2520091614
02:30:22.579 --> 02:30:25.036
Those rights we know come
with a responsibility.

1185484670
02:30:25.037 --> 02:30:27.177
A responsibility that Digwa has betrayed,

2447019060
02:30:27.178 --> 02:30:29.934
and he must now serve his
well- deserved punishment.

1555212320
02:30:29.935 --> 02:30:32.877
Of course, as other members have said,

3371915524
02:30:32.878 --> 02:30:35.538
we are too aware of
the tragedies of knife crime and

763244981
02:30:35.539 --> 02:30:38.749
the problem it represents in this
country that must be tackled,

43444831
02:30:38.750 --> 02:30:40.355
as Mark Nowak has rightly said.

3619375713
02:30:40.356 --> 02:30:42.413
The judge's remarks in this case tell us

2023467046
02:30:42.414 --> 02:30:44.621
the knife being carried
by the murderer was

1776888548
02:30:44.622 --> 02:30:46.978
different to that typically
carried by British

3741038153
02:30:46.979 --> 02:30:48.585
seats as a part of their faith.

120737508
02:30:48.586 --> 02:30:52.048
>> It's no use holding your hand up
as though you're some policemen.

1070715243
02:30:52.049 --> 02:30:54.810
I'm placing it on the time
given you quite a bit over.

1655199227
02:30:54.811 --> 02:30:56.668
I hope you're coming to the end now.

2450240852
02:30:56.669 --> 02:30:57.322
>> I am, Mr.

1417475073
02:30:57.323 --> 02:30:58.626
Speaker, and I apologise.

3342760800
02:30:58.627 --> 02:31:01.588
As Mark Nowak has said,
the outcome here should be one of.

4271306069
02:31:01.589 --> 02:31:02.039
Further.

2622875945
02:31:02.040 --> 02:31:03.996
Should not be one of further division.

370837705
02:31:03.997 --> 02:31:05.903
In that spirit and in Henry's memory,

1204292266
02:31:05.904 --> 02:31:08.162
we must work together
to ensure this kind of

2332003099
02:31:08.163 --> 02:31:10.278
tragedy is not allowed to happen again.

3853950320
02:31:10.279 --> 02:31:11.182
>> Thank you, Mr.

106180401
02:31:11.183 --> 02:31:11.633
Speaker.

913873580
02:31:11.634 --> 02:31:18.376
Well, let me say I welcome
the contribution from the Liberal Democrat

1113813551
02:31:18.377 --> 02:31:21.034
spokesman and associate
myself with his words again,

4030052709
02:31:21.035 --> 02:31:25.483
in relation to the family and their
reaction to what has happened.

2399586060
02:31:25.484 --> 02:31:28.494
I'm not sure there was a specific
question in there for me,

2305851675
02:31:28.496 --> 02:31:32.194
but if there are other things that
the member wishes to pick up with me,

1040372247
02:31:32.195 --> 02:31:35.257
then I'd be very happy to to
engage with him on other points

688083350
02:31:35.258 --> 02:31:37.932
of detail that maybe he
wasn't able to come on to.

658404500
02:31:37.933 --> 02:31:41.094
Let me just reiterate, for
the benefit of the whole House, Mr.

970247841
02:31:41.095 --> 02:31:44.678
Speaker, anyone using this
tragedy, this horrific,

3911222020
02:31:44.679 --> 02:31:48.378
vile act of murder in order to stoke
further division in our country,

2187972636
02:31:48.380 --> 02:31:51.278
should be rejected by
everyone across this House.

3340509825
02:31:51.279 --> 02:31:54.688
Political grandstanding and further
division is not what is needed.

446335490
02:31:54.689 --> 02:31:58.085
Clear eyed action and a commitment
to ensuring all of our citizens

1983065454
02:31:58.086 --> 02:32:02.726
are equal before the law of our
collective land is what is needed.

2454859421
02:32:02.726 --> 02:32:03.730
>> Clive Efford Mr.

3239422706
02:32:03.731 --> 02:32:09.430
Speaker, this is
a terrible incident and my

3000816512
02:32:09.431 --> 02:32:12.981
heart goes out to the family of Henry.

397488227
02:32:12.982 --> 02:32:14.036
But is my right hon.

3953064219
02:32:14.928 --> 02:32:17.336
Friend concerned as I am,
that some have raised

3553903036
02:32:17.337 --> 02:32:19.583
the issue of the Macpherson inquiry,

200384029
02:32:19.583 --> 02:32:23.179
and that this has caused the police
to hold back when dealing with

4079291091
02:32:23.180 --> 02:32:26.779
people who perpetrate crimes who
may be from an ethnic minority.

3067626229
02:32:26.780 --> 02:32:30.640
And she agree with me that there
is nothing in the Macpherson

2816281188
02:32:30.641 --> 02:32:34.286
inquiry that suggests the police
should behave in that way,

2888994087
02:32:34.287 --> 02:32:38.011
or excuses the extraordinary behaviour of

1262969055
02:32:38.012 --> 02:32:39.969
the police at the scene of this crime.

4218136183
02:32:39.970 --> 02:32:43.282
And does she think that that what
needs reviewing here is the way

2571185862
02:32:43.283 --> 02:32:46.493
that police are trained in dealing
with incidents of this sort,

279692000
02:32:46.494 --> 02:32:50.108
because it seems to me that there was
a that that that what happened at

4186480245
02:32:50.109 --> 02:32:54.237
the scene of that crime falls way
below what we expect of the police.

856152832
02:32:54.238 --> 02:32:55.493
>> Well, I thank my hon.

580534460
02:32:55.494 --> 02:32:55.894
Friend.

2035681916
02:32:55.895 --> 02:32:59.431
Let me say, look, police officers
must apply the law fairly without

2506871433
02:32:59.928 --> 02:33:03.278
fear or favour to every single
person that they serve.

377438802
02:33:03.279 --> 02:33:06.124
They do work incredibly
hard and they do get

2176437457
02:33:06.125 --> 02:33:08.132
it right the vast majority of the time.

1777467082
02:33:08.133 --> 02:33:10.440
But where mistakes are
made, it is right that

2863293430
02:33:10.442 --> 02:33:12.731
they are properly
investigated and examined.

49610002
02:33:12.732 --> 02:33:16.378
I do think the whole House should
remember that our police officers

208145674
02:33:16.378 --> 02:33:19.931
every day run towards danger in
order to keep our community safe.

2186356637
02:33:19.932 --> 02:33:22.989
He will know on the specifics
of this case because

919142970
02:33:22.990 --> 02:33:25.345
of the ongoing independent
IOPC investigation,

2901409319
02:33:25.346 --> 02:33:27.452
I don't think it's appropriate to comment

534316907
02:33:27.453 --> 02:33:30.184
further on the specifics of this case.

313513429
02:33:30.185 --> 02:33:31.590
>> Father of the House sir.

3833158384
02:33:31.591 --> 02:33:32.292
Edward Leigh.

94032307
02:33:32.293 --> 02:33:34.901
>> I agree with everything
the Home Secretary says,

172424918
02:33:34.902 --> 02:33:37.510
and I agree that we shouldn't
weaponise this issue,

159856289
02:33:37.511 --> 02:33:39.317
but nor should we tiptoe around it.

2819751603
02:33:39.318 --> 02:33:42.595
The truth is that many white
people in this country feel

2038244557
02:33:42.928 --> 02:33:46.278
that the police are so terrified
of being called racist

916583014
02:33:46.279 --> 02:33:48.285
that either they underreact in the case

4093059511
02:33:48.928 --> 02:33:50.682
of the appalling grooming scandal,

4135263365
02:33:50.683 --> 02:33:53.134
or they overreact in this case.

2905873217
02:33:53.135 --> 02:33:55.480
So there is a role for the Home Secretary.

1660121295
02:33:55.481 --> 02:33:59.682
Now she needs to really summon in
these top police officers and say,

4195469301
02:33:59.683 --> 02:34:03.479
things have got to change.

4128306839
02:34:03.480 --> 02:34:04.383
We are all equal.

280459503
02:34:04.384 --> 02:34:06.942
Don't be terrified of what
people think about you.

1421632452
02:34:06.943 --> 02:34:12.390
Just carry out the law as you're
supposed to do as police officers.

2235862568
02:34:12.391 --> 02:34:13.128
>> Mr.

2233541717
02:34:13.128 --> 02:34:16.579
speaker, I have made very
clear from this Dispatch Box

83243354
02:34:16.580 --> 02:34:20.235
and over the course of my tenure
as Home Secretary to say all

4029214662
02:34:20.237 --> 02:34:24.483
are equal before the law
and the police must always act

4093940686
02:34:24.484 --> 02:34:27.242
without fear and without
favour towards any one group.

4280804903
02:34:27.243 --> 02:34:31.545
I don't think it's helpful for us
to start pitting either majority

12260247
02:34:31.546 --> 02:34:35.579
or different minority communities
against one another.

1057371340
02:34:35.580 --> 02:34:38.590
That is not what this moment
requires, and it is important.

2741027980
02:34:38.591 --> 02:34:39.192
He's right.

153253178
02:34:39.193 --> 02:34:41.149
There's always a balance to be struck.

1816322131
02:34:41.150 --> 02:34:43.906
There mustn't be underreaction
or indeed overreaction.

1249113321
02:34:43.907 --> 02:34:45.110
It is always a balance.

4186954857
02:34:45.112 --> 02:34:48.374
And I do believe that the police,
in the vast majority of cases,

2005030879
02:34:48.375 --> 02:34:49.729
do get that balance right.

3963073591
02:34:49.730 --> 02:34:52.289
And as I say, our police
officers every single day

2870599096
02:34:52.290 --> 02:34:54.548
run towards danger in
order to keep us safe.

1338992330
02:34:54.549 --> 02:34:58.178
I will always scrutinise all
these actions to make sure

1656089540
02:34:58.179 --> 02:35:00.988
that our police service is
functioning as it should be,

70831111
02:35:00.989 --> 02:35:03.378
so that every single
citizen in our country,

214096798
02:35:03.378 --> 02:35:05.485
regardless of the colour of their skin or

4113864390
02:35:05.928 --> 02:35:08.036
the faith that they have or may not have,

2069747557
02:35:08.037 --> 02:35:10.444
can be absolutely certain
that they will always

848230673
02:35:10.445 --> 02:35:12.300
be treated equally and that whatever

284261237
02:35:12.301 --> 02:35:14.707
complaint they have will
always be investigated

3678074488
02:35:14.708 --> 02:35:16.565
in the way that we would all expect.

233431701
02:35:16.565 --> 02:35:17.467
>> Amarjit Singh.

3813229317
02:35:17.469 --> 02:35:18.874
>> Thank you very much, Mr.

4141345099
02:35:18.875 --> 02:35:19.324
Speaker.

860158754
02:35:19.326 --> 02:35:22.031
I am deeply saddened by
the murder of Henry Nowak

1131270141
02:35:22.032 --> 02:35:25.681
and my heartfelt
condolences to his family,

3824642852
02:35:25.682 --> 02:35:27.539
whose pain was made all the worse by

2858208729
02:35:28.885 --> 02:35:30.789
the police wrongly handcuffing Henry,

3927194901
02:35:32.928 --> 02:35:35.134
believing the lies of
the violent murderer,

1625748834
02:35:35.135 --> 02:35:40.378
and that stripped Henry of his dignity
in his agonising final moments,

2029725404
02:35:40.380 --> 02:35:42.535
something which should never happen again.

2609670869
02:35:42.928 --> 02:35:43.630
But also, Mr.

1182437920
02:35:43.631 --> 02:35:48.233
Speaker, what's very galling
is that the likes of reform,

3260361699
02:35:48.234 --> 02:35:54.083
restore and the far right decided
to politicise people's pain,

1838162209
02:35:54.083 --> 02:35:57.483
attacking the Sikh community for wearing

4155597126
02:35:57.484 --> 02:36:00.436
the kirpan and wanting it banned.

1030806051
02:36:00.437 --> 02:36:05.135
Even though the kirpan was not
used in this violent attack,

3354375327
02:36:05.136 --> 02:36:10.139
and they've decided to scapegoat
and throw under the bus an entire

2233539926
02:36:10.932 --> 02:36:13.740
community based on the actions
of one violent murderer.

1347021796
02:36:14.929 --> 02:36:16.786
And let me also give them a history.

876047485
02:36:16.787 --> 02:36:20.135
>> Or you're meant to be
going through the chair,

2205118868
02:36:20.136 --> 02:36:21.934
not across the chamber.

2176143321
02:36:21.935 --> 02:36:22.988
>> My apologies, Mr.

1452672440
02:36:22.989 --> 02:36:27.988
Speaker, and let it not
be said that we see them,

1293758574
02:36:27.989 --> 02:36:31.194
and we will stand up to them.

1995337548
02:36:31.195 --> 02:36:31.596
And we.

3348000675
02:36:31.597 --> 02:36:34.583
Let me also give a short
history lesson, Mr.

743717037
02:36:34.583 --> 02:36:35.034
Speaker.

1923653965
02:36:35.035 --> 02:36:38.628
>> Order, order!

4227396302
02:36:38.628 --> 02:36:41.086
I started this session by
tolerance and respect,

2694208943
02:36:41.087 --> 02:36:42.944
and I don't expect to be pointing at

2765793061
02:36:42.945 --> 02:36:44.800
each other and attacking each other.

206646417
02:36:44.801 --> 02:36:46.884
You work through the chair.

1978665604
02:36:46.885 --> 02:36:49.528
We want an orderly chamber
that is respectful.

1012308927
02:36:49.529 --> 02:36:50.883
This does nobody any good.

1234334333
02:36:50.884 --> 02:36:51.335
I think.

1595787114
02:36:52.932 --> 02:36:53.885
>> Thank you very.

4162698372
02:36:53.886 --> 02:36:54.337
>> Much.

727886226
02:36:54.338 --> 02:36:54.689
>> Mr.

2452630347
02:36:54.690 --> 02:36:58.690
Speaker, because hundreds of
thousands of Sikh soldiers bravely

91583514
02:36:58.690 --> 02:37:01.783
fought alongside British
soldiers during both world wars,

1464676282
02:37:01.784 --> 02:37:04.934
tens of thousands made
the ultimate sacrifice,

2420527706
02:37:04.935 --> 02:37:08.633
proudly wearing their
turban and their kirpan.

1908387239
02:37:08.634 --> 02:37:10.590
So what reassurances can my right hon.

1379550089
02:37:10.591 --> 02:37:13.482
Friend the Home Secretary,
give to the Sikh community,

83010088
02:37:13.483 --> 02:37:17.684
which is both horrified
and ashamed at this brutal murder,

1420257095
02:37:17.685 --> 02:37:22.433
and they are fearful of
their right to freely

181264312
02:37:22.434 --> 02:37:24.288
and peacefully practice their faith.

138941052
02:37:24.932 --> 02:37:25.383
>> Well.

2644748077
02:37:25.384 --> 02:37:26.990
>> Let me reiterate for my hon.

3573089876
02:37:27.932 --> 02:37:30.238
Friend, religious freedom
is a very important

1106945842
02:37:30.239 --> 02:37:32.293
principle that this government respects,

182828839
02:37:32.294 --> 02:37:35.685
that has been respected
by different governments

879719169
02:37:35.686 --> 02:37:37.790
of different party political persuasions,

2591251701
02:37:37.791 --> 02:37:40.451
and I'm sure that that will
continue to be the case.

86469069
02:37:40.452 --> 02:37:42.482
As I said in my statement,

1300226272
02:37:42.483 --> 02:37:46.378
we are not a country that
collectively punishes

2266145776
02:37:46.378 --> 02:37:49.582
an entire group of people for
the actions of individuals.

4012977934
02:37:49.583 --> 02:37:52.591
The responsibility for this
murder rests with the murderer,

2100610929
02:37:52.592 --> 02:37:56.335
and he has now faced justice
and been sentenced,

3591535846
02:37:56.336 --> 02:37:59.636
and that is the right way for
these matters to proceed.

4034230211
02:37:59.637 --> 02:38:01.683
Let me also say something, Mr.

891593890
02:38:01.684 --> 02:38:03.540
Speaker, on the tone of this debate,

1100825936
02:38:03.935 --> 02:38:07.884
I think it's it would be right
for the whole House to remember.

4123309461
02:38:07.885 --> 02:38:10.794
I'm sure Henry Nowak family
and his friends are watching,

4171602983
02:38:10.795 --> 02:38:13.404
and the way we conduct
ourselves in this place can,

1796559839
02:38:13.405 --> 02:38:14.708
of course, be passionate,

3411691759
02:38:15.939 --> 02:38:19.083
but must not result in
name calling and also in

3103041945
02:38:19.083 --> 02:38:21.389
just shouting different
political views here,

1310872413
02:38:21.934 --> 02:38:24.041
because I don't think we should all stand

3862989938
02:38:24.042 --> 02:38:26.485
for a politicisation of this murder.

1723959050
02:38:26.487 --> 02:38:33.232
There are lessons to be learned
and I'm sure further issues to be drawn

1445342932
02:38:33.233 --> 02:38:36.743
from what has happened once the IOPC
has concluded its investigation,

783813407
02:38:36.744 --> 02:38:39.605
I'm sure we will debate them
here in the future as well.

3442587047
02:38:39.606 --> 02:38:42.064
But the way that we conduct
that debate matters,

2754401522
02:38:42.065 --> 02:38:44.739
matters just as much, in
my view, as what is, said.

829695315
02:38:44.740 --> 02:38:45.642
>> Lewis Cocking.

2254143315
02:38:45.643 --> 02:38:46.546
>> Thank you, Mr.

160543165
02:38:46.547 --> 02:38:46.997
Speaker.

3688508011
02:38:46.998 --> 02:38:49.738
>> This is an appalling
and sickening tragedy.

315014052
02:38:49.739 --> 02:38:51.333
>> Words cannot.

1586347890
02:38:51.335 --> 02:38:52.487
Express my heartbreak.

3525890958
02:38:52.488 --> 02:38:55.851
>> For Henry's family and fury at
the system that has led to this.

2029009130
02:38:55.932 --> 02:38:57.789
We have all seen the body worn video

2959879095
02:38:57.790 --> 02:39:00.597
and in a previous role, as part of my job,

1592251795
02:39:00.598 --> 02:39:05.482
it was my job to review that footage
and give an independent judgement.

2503263701
02:39:05.483 --> 02:39:09.483
In this case, it is clear
to everyone that the police

4215032180
02:39:09.484 --> 02:39:13.033
did not use appropriate
and proportionate action.

2907913650
02:39:13.034 --> 02:39:16.489
There are many good police officers
who work hard to keep us safe,

1125330159
02:39:16.490 --> 02:39:19.649
but on that night, those police
officers displayed no concern.

3513419395
02:39:19.650 --> 02:39:20.283
For Henry.

2829940890
02:39:20.284 --> 02:39:24.232
Immediate actions should have been taken

1132524012
02:39:24.233 --> 02:39:26.190
to try and save his life, but instead,

843842382
02:39:26.190 --> 02:39:30.189
Henry was put in handcuffs
and mocked as he lay dying.

1378118423
02:39:30.892 --> 02:39:33.699
Those police officers have
serious questions to answer.

765748811
02:39:34.932 --> 02:39:37.088
Can the Home Secretary explain what action

150510740
02:39:37.089 --> 02:39:39.296
the government will now
take to ensure that

3489524149
02:39:39.297 --> 02:39:41.452
every officer involved is held accountable

4214911413
02:39:41.453 --> 02:39:43.409
for the decisions that they have made,

2675085064
02:39:43.410 --> 02:39:45.980
and so that the public
can have confidence that

2207707006
02:39:45.981 --> 02:39:50.089
we'll all be treated
equally under the law?

3351069533
02:39:50.090 --> 02:39:50.741
>> Secondly.

63803117
02:39:50.742 --> 02:39:54.137
>> Well, let me let me give the hon.

458242544
02:39:54.137 --> 02:39:56.645
Gentleman that assurance
by referring to the fact

3209336021
02:39:56.646 --> 02:40:00.244
that the Iopc is
investigating this matter,

2018698827
02:40:00.244 --> 02:40:02.202
and they will be free to conclude that

361060757
02:40:02.203 --> 02:40:04.108
investigation using all of the powers

3716175298
02:40:04.936 --> 02:40:08.296
that they have and also all of their
evidence gathering abilities.

1790562988
02:40:08.297 --> 02:40:11.357
He will know, having reviewed
such such footage in the past.

1179637158
02:40:11.358 --> 02:40:13.414
Of course, what is publicly available is

3085205196
02:40:13.415 --> 02:40:15.471
three minutes of a much longer incident,

31561149
02:40:15.472 --> 02:40:19.491
but the Iopc will be able to review
every bit of body cam footage,

3329950473
02:40:19.492 --> 02:40:21.432
all of it in its totality,

3898351256
02:40:21.433 --> 02:40:23.289
as well as other evidence that sheds

3684660405
02:40:23.290 --> 02:40:26.491
light on the context of the incident

1498638816
02:40:26.492 --> 02:40:30.342
and also what the police officers
saw and how they reacted to it.

3290460778
02:40:30.344 --> 02:40:33.905
The Iopc is free to make recommendations
not just on specific conduct,

2303363591
02:40:33.906 --> 02:40:37.039
but also on wider lessons
that should be drawn.

2214563399
02:40:37.040 --> 02:40:38.092
Let me reassure him.

833022024
02:40:38.094 --> 02:40:40.601
Once the Iopc has reported
and made its findings,

2908210316
02:40:40.603 --> 02:40:43.262
I will make sure that
I personally update the House.

930565954
02:40:43.262 --> 02:40:46.190
>> Jen Craft thank you, Mr.

1095868961
02:40:46.192 --> 02:40:46.642
Speaker.

3229723749
02:40:46.643 --> 02:40:50.142
I would like to pay tribute to
my constituent, Henry Nowak,

2231409512
02:40:50.143 --> 02:40:55.040
a bright young man at the start of
a life that held so much promise.

3791712030
02:40:55.041 --> 02:40:58.401
The turnout at his funeral and
the outpouring of community support

1377041903
02:40:58.402 --> 02:41:02.050
show that he had an impact
well beyond his young years.

2532675851
02:41:02.051 --> 02:41:04.993
I would like to pay tribute to his family,

4029174683
02:41:04.994 --> 02:41:06.848
Mark Nowak, particularly his father.

4111481979
02:41:06.849 --> 02:41:08.503
Many here have quoted his words,

860657694
02:41:08.505 --> 02:41:13.641
calling that Henry's death does not
lead to more division and hatred.

4130337748
02:41:13.642 --> 02:41:16.050
His sister, Olivia made
space in the early days

2052223717
02:41:16.051 --> 02:41:18.341
of her own grief to
support Henry's friends.

511692875
02:41:18.342 --> 02:41:21.001
I think that speaks to this
family and their courage

2962294663
02:41:21.002 --> 02:41:24.389
and their bravery
and their dignity in dealing

2224610775
02:41:24.390 --> 02:41:26.948
with one of the most tragic
and devastating things

2459055580
02:41:26.949 --> 02:41:29.636
that any of us could ever
imagine going through.

643100036
02:41:29.637 --> 02:41:32.846
Like many in this House,
I've watched the body worn

102346312
02:41:32.847 --> 02:41:35.404
video camera footage that
was released last night,

463544021
02:41:35.405 --> 02:41:37.143
and I watched it with horror.

3938715840
02:41:37.144 --> 02:41:40.003
I could not imagine what Henry's
family felt seeing that

2564606201
02:41:40.003 --> 02:41:42.612
and knowing that that was
their son's last moments.

3070167586
02:41:42.613 --> 02:41:44.788
They expected help from the police.

3161137523
02:41:44.789 --> 02:41:47.337
But when Henry lay dying, what he got was

3507384313
02:41:47.338 --> 02:41:49.092
accusation and he was disbelieved.

33944432
02:41:49.092 --> 02:41:52.140
This can never happen again.

3196305290
02:41:52.141 --> 02:41:54.349
I would like to ask
the Home Secretary what

3846417515
02:41:54.350 --> 02:41:57.737
she will do to meet
Henry's family's calls.

3409444268
02:41:57.738 --> 02:42:01.149
First of all, to tackle the national
emergency that is knife crime.

3272491315
02:42:01.150 --> 02:42:05.282
Like many families who have suffered
a loss from this appalling crime,

4185302749
02:42:05.283 --> 02:42:08.494
Henry's family have called that
his death has not been in vain,

2024851955
02:42:08.494 --> 02:42:12.194
that lessons are learned,
and that they can go forward to see

3717725029
02:42:12.195 --> 02:42:15.307
that his legacy is that no one
else has to suffer that grief.

4287739058
02:42:15.937 --> 02:42:19.737
And secondly, I would welcome
the Home Secretary's assurances that

2384525396
02:42:19.738 --> 02:42:23.047
the Iopc investigation will be
thorough, will be fully resourced,

1482953616
02:42:23.048 --> 02:42:25.089
that no stone will be left unturned,

3531070611
02:42:25.090 --> 02:42:28.692
that the family will have
the answers they need and deserve.

3010794185
02:42:28.693 --> 02:42:31.503
They will know why their son
was treated as a criminal,

3286937568
02:42:31.503 --> 02:42:33.440
and why the criminal was treated with

1393538130
02:42:33.440 --> 02:42:35.939
much more dignity than their son was,

2839167564
02:42:35.940 --> 02:42:38.536
and I would be grateful if she would speak

1551494684
02:42:38.537 --> 02:42:40.443
to make sure that the family's needs,

530283016
02:42:40.940 --> 02:42:46.188
their wishes, and that their voices
are heard throughout this inquiry.

1988511236
02:42:46.189 --> 02:42:47.092
>> Thank you, Mr.

1040933092
02:42:47.092 --> 02:42:47.543
Speaker.

3761089118
02:42:47.544 --> 02:42:49.351
Let me first pay tribute to my hon.

293128490
02:42:49.351 --> 02:42:52.790
Friend for her powerful
contribution as Henry's

3642069990
02:42:52.791 --> 02:42:57.038
constituency member of Parliament.

4238132546
02:42:57.039 --> 02:42:59.747
Let me firstly give her
absolutely the assurance that

1423346167
02:42:59.748 --> 02:43:04.744
she seeks in relation to
the Iopc investigation,

820419631
02:43:04.744 --> 02:43:07.654
and I know that that investigation
is continuing at pace.

1945659371
02:43:07.655 --> 02:43:09.963
I know that the family
is being engaged with.

3326366411
02:43:09.964 --> 02:43:12.791
If there are any concerns
about that process,

3830804626
02:43:12.792 --> 02:43:17.493
I do invite her to let me know
immediately and I will personally

1422008071
02:43:17.494 --> 02:43:21.391
ensure that any concerns
are dealt with and that

240156642
02:43:21.392 --> 02:43:25.484
the family can have confidence
in the Iopc process.

2237582965
02:43:25.485 --> 02:43:27.091
Let me say also on knife crime,

1629646869
02:43:27.092 --> 02:43:29.848
this government has acknowledged
the absolute epidemic

3277081566
02:43:29.849 --> 02:43:31.756
of knife crime in our country and the

1000951747
02:43:31.757 --> 02:43:34.943
the imperative that we
have to act upon it.

3882391045
02:43:34.944 --> 02:43:37.000
It's why we have our landmark commitment

2424782110
02:43:37.001 --> 02:43:38.807
to halve knife crime over a decade,

842968764
02:43:38.808 --> 02:43:41.587
why we have launched
the Knife Crime Action Plan.

2964542344
02:43:41.588 --> 02:43:43.895
It is a resource package
of measures designed

308454406
02:43:43.896 --> 02:43:46.291
to deal with the scourge of knife crime.

3129812953
02:43:46.292 --> 02:43:48.198
And let me give her this reassurance.

3064996157
02:43:48.199 --> 02:43:50.557
And exactly as I said in
my statement earlier,

3164845000
02:43:50.558 --> 02:43:54.592
we will leave no stone unturned to
deal with knife crime in our country,

45251796
02:43:54.592 --> 02:43:59.994
and we do so in the name of all victims
of knife crime, including Henry.

181141291
02:43:59.994 --> 02:44:03.456
Their lives must not be in vain,
and we must learn the lessons

2136624554
02:44:03.457 --> 02:44:06.693
that prevent these tragedies
from occurring in the future.

225940807
02:44:06.694 --> 02:44:07.646
>> Robert Jenrick.

1506617838
02:44:07.646 --> 02:44:08.600
>> When Henry lay.

2476102333
02:44:08.601 --> 02:44:11.942
>> On the floor, he warned that
he had been stabbed four times.

1124172031
02:44:11.943 --> 02:44:14.940
He said that he couldn't
breathe nine times,

2717987237
02:44:14.940 --> 02:44:18.538
and yet the officer chose to
cuff him rather than treat him.

1947207067
02:44:18.539 --> 02:44:21.596
That officer should be in court,

3339086346
02:44:21.597 --> 02:44:24.987
being prosecuted for
a total dereliction of duty.

1700676578
02:44:24.988 --> 02:44:28.744
But the bigger question is this why
do officers behave in this way?

42129255
02:44:28.746 --> 02:44:35.690
Is it because they have been taught
repeatedly to elevate perceptions of

1361526878
02:44:35.692 --> 02:44:40.544
ethnic minority communities over
the safety of white British people?

302139352
02:44:40.545 --> 02:44:43.339
That sickness contributed to the killings

2722487269
02:44:43.340 --> 02:44:45.687
of Rudy Cabana of Caledon in Nottingham,

2068241766
02:44:45.688 --> 02:44:50.644
and now to Digwa is a sickness
rooted in the anti-racism agenda.

2876926034
02:44:50.645 --> 02:44:54.089
Will the Home Secretary root it out?

309266467
02:44:54.090 --> 02:44:57.144
Will she return to equality
before the law for all?

2191520601
02:44:57.145 --> 02:45:01.502
And will she say that when
it comes to public safety,

4223924064
02:45:01.503 --> 02:45:04.847
white lives matter just
as much as anyone else's?

3849201530
02:45:04.848 --> 02:45:05.299
>> Hear.

3237827703
02:45:07.940 --> 02:45:08.642
>> Hear, sir.

3237934935
02:45:08.643 --> 02:45:09.546
>> Thank you, Mr.

3222543201
02:45:09.547 --> 02:45:09.997
Speaker.

2497799544
02:45:09.998 --> 02:45:13.743
Let me say to the hon.

2952697925
02:45:13.744 --> 02:45:16.542
Gentleman, I don't think
this is a moment to

3409499583
02:45:16.543 --> 02:45:20.390
pit white Britons against
non-white Britons.

3466461954
02:45:20.391 --> 02:45:23.390
This is a moment to reflect
on a horrific tragedy.

333310151
02:45:23.391 --> 02:45:25.899
He knows full well that
the Iopc is investigating

3776575668
02:45:25.900 --> 02:45:27.805
the conduct of those police officers.

1664284128
02:45:27.940 --> 02:45:31.449
It would be wholly inappropriate
for a member of this House

4167764160
02:45:31.449 --> 02:45:35.895
to seek to pre-empt
an independent investigation into

3866061005
02:45:35.896 --> 02:45:39.243
the the potential misconduct
of police officers that IOPC

1993032291
02:45:39.244 --> 02:45:42.594
investigation will look at
individual conduct, but also.

1832043621
02:45:42.595 --> 02:45:46.197
What are the wider lessons can
be learned from this case?

3751762294
02:45:46.198 --> 02:45:49.945
I will personally ensure that all lessons

1213778588
02:45:49.946 --> 02:45:52.094
are learned and indeed acted upon.

4045230617
02:45:52.095 --> 02:45:55.293
And let me also say it is
a fundamental principle

1339541479
02:45:55.294 --> 02:45:58.196
not just of the British
criminal justice system,

537902754
02:45:58.197 --> 02:46:00.105
but who and what we are as a country,

2131862287
02:46:00.106 --> 02:46:02.616
that we are all equal
before the law of our land.

3675414143
02:46:02.617 --> 02:46:05.225
That applies regardless of
the colour of your skin.

1523067932
02:46:05.226 --> 02:46:07.991
That applies whether you're
a non-white Brit whose

2259776527
02:46:07.992 --> 02:46:10.693
family arrived here 50 years
ago or ten years ago,

1518695112
02:46:10.694 --> 02:46:12.902
or if you're a white
Brit whose family have

218723236
02:46:12.903 --> 02:46:14.860
been here for about 300 years or more.

1466856403
02:46:14.860 --> 02:46:17.070
We are all equal before
the law of our land

324111708
02:46:17.071 --> 02:46:19.695
and we should all support that principle,

1556732642
02:46:19.696 --> 02:46:22.808
but not use it so as to pit our
citizens against one another.

1668915784
02:46:22.809 --> 02:46:25.444
That is not what this moment demands.

4001360303
02:46:25.445 --> 02:46:28.143
>> Florence Eshalomi thank you, Mr.

3662839857
02:46:28.144 --> 02:46:31.455
Speaker, and I thank the Home
Secretary for coming to the chamber

3468837250
02:46:31.456 --> 02:46:34.548
this afternoon and and as many
Honourable and right hon.

1489207064
02:46:34.549 --> 02:46:38.591
Members have said, no one can be
moved after watching that footage

3887281283
02:46:38.592 --> 02:46:42.842
and and just seeing a young
life being wasted like that.

2454594952
02:46:42.842 --> 02:46:46.189
But I think just inhumane
and degrading treatment that

3996350055
02:46:46.190 --> 02:46:48.649
Henry had to go through
in his last few moments.

2499912082
02:46:48.650 --> 02:46:51.007
It's something that will
stay with the family,

1886166315
02:46:51.008 --> 02:46:53.064
something that will stay with the family

766065111
02:46:53.065 --> 02:46:54.921
when the news coverage has moved on,

2220660176
02:46:54.922 --> 02:46:57.279
something that will stay
with the family after

2568371910
02:46:57.280 --> 02:46:59.485
those police officers
have been prosecuted.

257139076
02:46:59.485 --> 02:47:04.892
Because when someone is killed by
a murderer who is intent on killing,

743016637
02:47:04.893 --> 02:47:06.146
regardless of your race,

2442138492
02:47:06.146 --> 02:47:08.354
it is the families
and the communities that

1631299218
02:47:08.355 --> 02:47:10.362
have to deal with the long term impact.

1862275370
02:47:10.363 --> 02:47:13.373
Many of us in this chamber have
had to comfort constituents

2125926414
02:47:13.374 --> 02:47:15.831
who've lost a family member
through knife crime,

1897858377
02:47:15.832 --> 02:47:18.592
and this epidemic across
the UK has to come to a stop.

764123092
02:47:18.594 --> 02:47:23.791
How is it possible that this killer
was allowed to roam the streets

2698676098
02:47:23.792 --> 02:47:27.645
with the 21 centimetre knife
and freely stab someone and then lie?

2770865459
02:47:27.646 --> 02:47:30.105
It is really important
that we do make sure that

625121942
02:47:30.106 --> 02:47:32.162
this government gets to grips with that.

3049558045
02:47:32.163 --> 02:47:38.151
So I want to ask the Home Secretary
as soon as the IOPC conclude

3978603264
02:47:38.152 --> 02:47:40.860
and find the find the findings
of this investigation,

199457666
02:47:40.860 --> 02:47:44.223
will she come back to this House
and make sure that the government

3407006830
02:47:44.224 --> 02:47:47.997
adequately responds so that
we are not back here again,

3062038650
02:47:47.998 --> 02:47:50.507
having to to to answer
and try to console another

3631966589
02:47:50.508 --> 02:47:54.047
family whose life has been
taken by knife crime.

1757493040
02:47:54.048 --> 02:47:54.749
>> Secretary.

1657046361
02:47:54.750 --> 02:47:56.796
>> I thank my friend.

3177678987
02:47:56.797 --> 02:47:58.502
Let me give her that reassurance.

3311489532
02:47:58.503 --> 02:47:59.557
I think it is right.

1583206184
02:47:59.558 --> 02:48:02.454
Whilst the Iopc investigation
is taking place,

3322749900
02:48:02.455 --> 02:48:05.649
that we give that the space it
needs to do its important work

3884376249
02:48:05.650 --> 02:48:08.260
and it will be wholly wrong
for Ministers to try to

4167810718
02:48:08.261 --> 02:48:11.101
pre-empt what findings might
be made in the future.

3349889878
02:48:11.101 --> 02:48:13.109
But as soon as those findings are made,

3472771950
02:48:13.110 --> 02:48:15.994
I will ensure the government responds.

2557410197
02:48:15.996 --> 02:48:18.003
>> Paul Holmes thank you very much, Mr.

444413895
02:48:18.003 --> 02:48:20.912
Speaker, and can I welcome
the Home Secretary's statement

3329213864
02:48:20.913 --> 02:48:22.970
this afternoon and just say that I think

2850156712
02:48:22.971 --> 02:48:25.230
we all in this House
need to be careful that

2583798093
02:48:25.231 --> 02:48:27.440
our response to what
is a sad loss of life,

2584149749
02:48:27.440 --> 02:48:32.653
of a young man who was going to
a vibrant university in a fantastic

451315315
02:48:32.654 --> 02:48:36.166
and welcoming city with the rest of
his life supposedly ahead of him,

924206381
02:48:36.167 --> 02:48:38.673
notwithstanding what
the Home Secretary has said,

2065920050
02:48:38.674 --> 02:48:40.530
and I'm grateful for her saying that

4085370499
02:48:40.531 --> 02:48:42.796
the Iopc will receive full resourcing,

3502113100
02:48:42.797 --> 02:48:46.998
has she done any thinking as to what
other investigations her department

2717973768
02:48:46.999 --> 02:48:50.645
might need to do into the conduct
of Hampshire Constabulary?

3764187258
02:48:50.646 --> 02:48:54.394
Can she confirm whether
the officers in question

2081015484
02:48:54.395 --> 02:48:56.750
have been suspended pending
the investigation?

3352959127
02:48:56.751 --> 02:48:59.358
And also, could she outline
whether she's currently

4191524283
02:48:59.359 --> 02:49:01.265
looking at whether she needs to needs

843987211
02:49:01.266 --> 02:49:03.851
to make changes to
the exemptions to carrying

3834361579
02:49:03.853 --> 02:49:07.547
knives for religious or cultural purposes?

4069302599
02:49:07.548 --> 02:49:08.500
>> Home Secretary.

2308110839
02:49:08.944 --> 02:49:09.948
>> I thank the hon.

332929713
02:49:09.949 --> 02:49:13.547
Member for for his contribution
and his questions.

2900758172
02:49:13.548 --> 02:49:16.196
Let me say to him, on
the question of suspensions,

1117548550
02:49:16.197 --> 02:49:19.399
that is a matter for
the Iopc because of the way that

2365079179
02:49:19.400 --> 02:49:22.007
they make their initial
findings and then obviously

2826285496
02:49:22.008 --> 02:49:24.565
react to the evidence as
it all becomes available.

4240232949
02:49:24.567 --> 02:49:27.826
And of course, now that the criminal
proceedings have concluded,

2346718815
02:49:28.899 --> 02:49:32.796
they will be able to ramp up
and go faster on, on, on that process.

2491247186
02:49:32.797 --> 02:49:36.548
So again, it wouldn't be
appropriate for Ministers to be

2195340635
02:49:36.549 --> 02:49:40.449
either cited on that or seek
to direct it in any way.

3237096257
02:49:40.451 --> 02:49:44.349
But, but I know that, you know,
staff at the Iopc are watching.

2557222729
02:49:44.350 --> 02:49:47.146
And to the extent that
there are clarifications

3676922689
02:49:47.148 --> 02:49:48.851
or questions that need answering,

577372391
02:49:48.853 --> 02:49:51.010
I'm sure that they will they will respond,

2268836945
02:49:51.011 --> 02:49:54.296
but they are wholly
independent of government.

4155075243
02:49:54.297 --> 02:49:59.849
Let me say to him, on the exemptions
for the carrying of knives

4025999854
02:49:59.850 --> 02:50:05.056
for the purposes of religious
ceremonial purposes,

519713729
02:50:05.057 --> 02:50:09.094
this has been a long standing
part of our arrangements as

1677567029
02:50:09.095 --> 02:50:12.895
a way of balancing public safety
alongside religious freedom.

1436083069
02:50:12.896 --> 02:50:17.446
It has been supported by, you
know, successive governments,

1168669792
02:50:17.447 --> 02:50:18.449
including this one.

1265165496
02:50:18.944 --> 02:50:20.952
So we are not seeking to move away from

2365948559
02:50:20.953 --> 02:50:24.498
our respect for religious freedom.

1109347517
02:50:24.499 --> 02:50:27.648
The wider sort of context
is an important question.

4179176222
02:50:27.649 --> 02:50:31.054
It is always worth serious consideration.

772829025
02:50:31.055 --> 02:50:33.896
But for myself, I think
my approach here will

3947054534
02:50:33.896 --> 02:50:36.744
be to engage directly with representatives

1636707316
02:50:36.744 --> 02:50:39.653
from the Sikh community
and also knife crime campaigners.

3829608427
02:50:39.654 --> 02:50:42.645
I think these are issues
of a common cause.

2063870480
02:50:42.646 --> 02:50:47.347
Rather than pitting those two
groups against one another.

3686229864
02:50:47.348 --> 02:50:50.650
But I would just repeat
the point I made in my statement.

3762034966
02:50:50.651 --> 02:50:53.059
There is a world of
difference between a person

2577056067
02:50:53.060 --> 02:50:55.045
acting out of religious observance,

1894188421
02:50:55.046 --> 02:50:57.294
carrying something as an act of faith,

940720472
02:50:57.295 --> 02:51:01.257
and somebody unsheathing that weapon
and using it to kill somebody.

2275721574
02:51:01.258 --> 02:51:04.500
And that individual has met
the full force of the law.

2399367592
02:51:04.501 --> 02:51:06.206
>> Jonathan Hinder thank you, Mr.

3338178448
02:51:06.207 --> 02:51:06.657
Speaker.

2674783914
02:51:06.658 --> 02:51:08.747
As you know, there is no bigger champion

2629458811
02:51:08.748 --> 02:51:12.145
for policing in this House than me,

2513512782
02:51:12.146 --> 02:51:16.146
but the body worn footage of Henry
Nowak death is gut wrenching,

3426950731
02:51:16.148 --> 02:51:19.600
and the police response is on the basis

439900296
02:51:19.601 --> 02:51:21.507
of what we know so far, unfathomable.

3067308867
02:51:21.508 --> 02:51:24.101
So it's right that
the Iopc is investigating,

2101937013
02:51:24.101 --> 02:51:27.601
but very often these investigations,

2831894937
02:51:27.603 --> 02:51:29.705
as everyone around policing knows,

2154601856
02:51:29.706 --> 02:51:34.046
have taken far, far too
long, sometimes many years,

3460651377
02:51:34.047 --> 02:51:36.053
which is not good for anybody involved.

2022597416
02:51:36.054 --> 02:51:40.653
So can the Home Secretary
assure me that she will

677306540
02:51:40.654 --> 02:51:45.595
press the Iopc to report
as quickly as possible?

3256869181
02:51:45.596 --> 02:51:47.251
Most of all, for Henry's family?

4026840095
02:51:47.949 --> 02:51:48.650
>> Secretary.

3128763341
02:51:48.651 --> 02:51:49.203
>> My hon.

3983555149
02:51:49.204 --> 02:51:52.711
Friend, speaks powerfully from deep
personal professional experience,

2250877068
02:51:54.948 --> 02:51:56.152
which I pay tribute to.

572726440
02:51:56.153 --> 02:52:00.351
Let me assure him that I, as
a constituency Member of Parliament,

1042748424
02:52:00.904 --> 02:52:03.161
have have had many
concerns about the length

2928459024
02:52:03.162 --> 02:52:06.351
of time it takes the Iopc sometimes

2726629460
02:52:06.353 --> 02:52:10.198
to report concerns that I've raised
with them directly since I've been

443088847
02:52:10.199 --> 02:52:13.309
Home Secretary on this occasion
and in relation to this case.

3372309331
02:52:13.310 --> 02:52:16.869
However, I do think, given that
the investigation started in December,

2280539468
02:52:16.871 --> 02:52:19.127
the criminal investigation
and case has only

661929519
02:52:19.128 --> 02:52:21.402
just concluded in
relation to the murderer.

453281274
02:52:21.403 --> 02:52:23.360
And given that the Iopc have said they

1519954628
02:52:23.360 --> 02:52:25.348
expect to report within three months,

3426150242
02:52:25.349 --> 02:52:29.605
I do believe that this this
investigation is proceeding

1738521404
02:52:29.606 --> 02:52:32.650
at the pace that this
House would would expect,

4187651335
02:52:32.651 --> 02:52:35.160
and I'm sure the IOPC are
reflecting on the tenor

1754882334
02:52:35.161 --> 02:52:37.498
of the debate today and will understand

414264123
02:52:37.499 --> 02:52:40.298
the need for urgency
and to make sure the family

2277964547
02:52:40.299 --> 02:52:42.706
have answers as quickly
as is humanly possible.

2398864733
02:52:42.948 --> 02:52:44.403
>> Liz Jarvis thank you, Mr.

3389704222
02:52:44.404 --> 02:52:44.854
Speaker.

2796324283
02:52:44.855 --> 02:52:47.853
My thoughts are with Henry Nowak family,

4007798356
02:52:47.854 --> 02:52:50.799
friends and the local community.

2774060146
02:52:50.800 --> 02:52:55.201
The prosecution said the perpetrator
had a weapons obsession.

2759523363
02:52:55.202 --> 02:52:58.252
