duties on sellers of knives

4174490680
02:53:35.449 --> 02:53:39.496
to report larger sales
or bulk sales of knives.

919381800
02:53:39.497 --> 02:53:42.507
The government has taken a broad
range of measures in order

1767923670
02:53:42.508 --> 02:53:45.318
