knife crime in our country.

4156773509
02:53:45.319 --> 02:53:47.174
Those measures have just become law.

3701892798
02:53:47.175 --> 02:53:49.884
We will ensure that the law
is implemented as quickly

1580707498
02:53:49.885 --> 02:53:52.546
as possible so that we can
get on top of this issue.

3531313711
02:53:52.547 --> 02:53:55.396
>> Sonia Kumar thank you, Mr.

689811954
02:53:55.396 --> 02:53:55.847
Speaker.

273426270
02:53:55.848 --> 02:53:58.356
The death of Henry Nowak
is a horrifying tragedy,

1158984464
02:53:58.357 --> 02:54:01.458
and my thoughts are with his
family, friends and community.

2548720970
02:54:01.460 --> 02:54:06.373
As a house, we use this tragedy to create

1798346490
02:54:06.374 --> 02:54:08.180
must honour the words of his father

4184786876
02:54:08.181 --> 02:54:12.550
not to use this tragedy to create
