1895952461
02:54:58.353 --> 02:55:02.162
and lessons can be learned by all
forces and then can be implemented.

1718535347
02:55:02.163 --> 02:55:03.115
>> Home Secretary.

3743650863
02:55:03.116 --> 02:55:04.399
>> The hon.

2953784913
02:55:04.400 --> 02:55:07.853
Lady makes a very good point,
and let me say to her that although

3142432707
02:55:07.854 --> 02:55:11.651
of course some of these
responsibilities are devolved, I.

1130819147
02:55:11.652 --> 02:55:13.508
I do hope that other legislatures in

2964053044
