4040537755
02:55:23.755 --> 02:55:25.560
>> Thank you, Madam Deputy Speaker,

1205629958
02:55:26.952 --> 02:55:31.864
and I also want to thank the Home
Secretary for her statement.

2833173376
02:55:31.865 --> 02:55:36.253
Madam Deputy Speaker, I seek
I wear the five K every day

3951474126
02:55:36.255 --> 02:55:42.152
part of my religious observance,
including the carbon.

790015554
02:55:42.153 --> 02:55:43.107
And as we seek, I.

1938228525
02:55:43.108 --> 02:55:48.249
I really struggle to express
the feelings of sheer

1024080495
02:55:48.250 --> 02:55:53.502
horror that this case has
generated within me,

1982353535
02:55:53.503 --> 02:55:55.260
my family and my my my my friends.

3450376466
02:55:55.261 --> 02:55:58.703
It is absolutely.

457626059
02:55:58.704 --> 02:55:59.707
It has been horror.

4105389111
02:55:59.708 --> 02:56:03.867
The senseless murder of Henry Nowak should

727241051
02:56:03.868 --> 02:56:06.024
be condemned in its entirety by everybody.

3129622128
02:56:06.025 --> 02:56:09.036
And you know, young man's life
