2292678802
02:56:09.037 --> 02:56:12.807
and I wish to express mine
and my constituency for

4293964726
02:56:12.808 --> 02:56:15.565
sympathy and condolences for
the family of Henry Nowak

176396116
02:56:17.970 --> 02:56:20.476
who have shown incredible
dignity in their grief.

67212008
02:56:21.952 --> 02:56:23.054
Madam Deputy Speaker.

2429183266
02:56:23.055 --> 02:56:27.056
I totally condemn the action
of Vickrum Digwa the.

1952035490
02:56:27.057 --> 02:56:27.758
The mindless.

1362326020
02:56:27.759 --> 02:56:31.012
The senseless murder, the lies and.

