4242260532
02:57:09.410 --> 02:57:13.054
And let me again emphasise the dignity

873622779
02:57:13.055 --> 02:57:15.753
and the grace shown by Henry's family.

429931730
02:57:15.753 --> 02:57:17.860
Their response has been something I don't

381333143
02:57:17.860 --> 02:57:19.565
believe I would have been capable

3658425021
02:57:19.567 --> 02:57:23.462
of if I had been in their shoes,
