4161950278
02:57:29.212 --> 02:57:31.317
Once the Iopc investigation is concluded,

2387336457
02:57:31.953 --> 02:57:36.305
we'll be able to draw further
conclusions as to the facts,

369451427
02:57:36.306 --> 02:57:39.854
the police response and
and wider problems as well.

2334207379
02:57:39.855 --> 02:57:42.202
Always happy to discuss with him the the,

242534110
02:57:42.203 --> 02:57:45.213
the the different nature of
the issues raised in this case,

2475629558
02:57:45.214 --> 02:57:47.322
and in particular on how we get the right

1393694641
02:57:47.323 --> 02:57:49.277
balance between the religious freedoms

2081652359
02:57:49.953 --> 02:57:54.304
that he and I both enjoy as members
of faith minorities in our country,

1612488959
02:57:54.305 --> 02:57:56.463
and also the need to make sure that public

815473349
02:57:56.464 --> 02:57:58.117
protection is never compromised.

75381481
02:57:58.118 --> 02:57:58.769
>> Morrison.

3366180460
02:57:58.770 --> 02:58:00.574
>> Thank you, Madam Deputy Speaker.

603718180
02:58:00.576 --> 02:58:02.431
Henry Nowak tragic murder was sadly,

2441774626
02:58:02.432 --> 02:58:05.210
