>> Yes.

928159196
02:58:29.365 --> 02:58:33.716
>> Let me reiterate my
belief and expectation

1239131893
02:58:33.717 --> 02:58:35.552
that the police must always

4285435098
02:58:35.553 --> 02:58:37.409
act without fear or favour and treat

1656553200
02:58:37.410 --> 02:58:39.606
all citizens equally before the law.

10423682
02:58:39.607 --> 02:58:42.065
I hope she will recognise
that the vast majority

1106388828
02:58:42.065 --> 02:58:44.355
of our police officers run towards

2863022190
02:58:44.356 --> 02:58:48.214
danger every day to keep us all safe,
and in the vast majority of cases,

1507768706
02:58:49.956 --> 02:58:52.564
they get the balance right
between how they respond

3687278890
02:58:52.565 --> 02:58:54.672
to a specific case and also more broadly,

1412775881
02:58:54.673 --> 02:58:56.359
how they keep communities safe.

4264951020
02:58:56.360 --> 02:58:58.817
Where there are issues,
lessons must be learned.

3742360328
02:58:58.818 --> 02:59:03.319
And I'm sure once the Iopc investigation
is concluded, we will do so.

2904095840
02:59:03.952 --> 02:59:05.606
Thank you, Madam Deputy Speaker.

2175691794
02:59:05.607 --> 02:59:07.503
I think for all of us as MPs,

2243188792
02:59:07.505 --> 02:59:10.408
the time we spend with
families who lose a family

2663539217
02:59:10.409 --> 02:59:13.918
member in horrific circumstances
stays with us throughout our career.

2506017139
02:59:13.919 --> 02:59:16.962
And I know in my community
there will be many parents

3990174045
02:59:16.963 --> 02:59:18.969
who sadly lost children to knife crime,

1474922269
02:59:18.970 --> 02:59:23.114
who will have seen Mark Nowak
statement and felt every single

3874682160
02:59:23.115 --> 02:59:25.874
word and want to send their
condolences to the family.

3324297701
02:59:25.912 --> 02:59:28.471
They will also be acutely
aware of how a difficult

3051118085
02:59:28.911 --> 02:59:30.716
watch that body camera footage was,

3863933092
02:59:30.717 --> 02:59:36.456
and his words about not seeing
