3272122201
02:59:56.079 --> 02:59:57.885
we need sources of light, not heat.

716758708
02:59:57.886 --> 03:00:00.669
What more could the Home
Office do on that matter?

450146632
03:00:00.670 --> 03:00:01.070
Please?

409442046
03:00:01.071 --> 03:00:04.859
Home Secretary well, let me say to my hon.

140621597
03:00:04.860 --> 03:00:07.467
Friend, we in the Home
Office have a responsibility

4054792794
03:00:07.469 --> 03:00:09.109
