3026025042
03:00:09.110 --> 03:00:12.108
to make sure that we act
calmly and responsibly

1267100095
03:00:12.109 --> 03:00:13.965
with the full facts at our disposal.

1940479029
03:00:13.966 --> 03:00:17.105
And if we do not have
the full facts at our disposal,

2197894072
03:00:17.106 --> 03:00:20.859
we wait until we do before
we comment so as not

1350243907
03:00:20.860 --> 03:00:23.908
to put out misleading
or false information.

503980595
03:00:23.909 --> 03:00:25.714
The wider environment she is right,

425530708
03:00:25.952 --> 03:00:29.359
is very challenging and of course
