03:00:50.213 --> 03:00:53.656
I think we have a responsibility
also in this House, collectively,

3437975916
03:00:53.657 --> 03:00:55.916
to make sure that we are
the ones that shine

648743029
03:00:55.917 --> 03:00:57.973
light rather than heat on these matters,

4104890715
03:00:57.974 --> 03:01:00.483
so that we can hold our
country together and make

3325662438
03:01:00.484 --> 03:01:02.992
sure that all of our
citizens are treated fairly.

3499631730
03:01:02.993 --> 03:01:04.356
>> Sammy Wilson.

3687155151
03:01:04.357 --> 03:01:07.618
