2062795161
03:01:26.311 --> 03:01:28.367
And this is something which is affecting

4090634010
03:01:28.368 --> 03:01:30.717
police right across the United Kingdom.

1576958991
03:01:30.717 --> 03:01:32.523
Only this week, in my constituency,

2563743228
03:01:32.524 --> 03:01:34.632
in a park on the edge of my constituency,

457156915
03:01:34.633 --> 03:01:38.215
