3744131249
03:01:40.411 --> 03:01:42.256
No arrests were made.

842365127
03:01:42.257 --> 03:01:44.614
Excuses were made for
the carrying of weapons,

3097265012
03:01:45.952 --> 03:01:50.162
and the anger of the community is
palpable, with the Secretary of State.

1379499641
03:01:50.163 --> 03:01:55.662
Make it clear to the police that
policing should be based on,

106814220
03:01:55.663 --> 03:02:01.373
