2380346499
03:02:01.374 --> 03:02:04.707
And it shouldn't be based on
the colour of people's skin.

1585941859
03:02:04.708 --> 03:02:05.108
People.

422458826
03:02:05.109 --> 03:02:07.953
Police should carry out
their duties impartially,

2208017415
03:02:07.954 --> 03:02:11.108
and two tier policing only
diminishes the police,

3866933999
03:02:11.109 --> 03:02:13.503
