2226725352
03:02:15.159 --> 03:02:17.061
which is bad for everybody.

887688270
03:02:17.062 --> 03:02:17.563
>> Great.

422498691
03:02:17.564 --> 03:02:19.911
>> Well, let me say to the hon.

3792855570
03:02:19.912 --> 03:02:23.523
Gentleman, there can, of course, be
