respond to danger every single

449120539
03:02:31.475 --> 03:02:36.416
day and have to make quick decisions
in very difficult circumstances.

1395307229
03:02:36.417 --> 03:02:39.478
And in the vast majority of
cases, they do get things right.

659891383
03:02:39.479 --> 03:02:41.987
And I do think it's important
that we acknowledge

986083764
03:02:41.988 --> 03:02:44.244
the broader picture in
relation to policing.

3485778667
03:02:44.244 --> 03:02:46.001
Of course, when things go wrong or

2973257996
03:02:46.002 --> 03:02:48.008
if the balance is not struck correctly,

3699344311
03:02:48.009 --> 03:02:49.657
that should be investigated,

278555860
03:02:49.658 --> 03:02:53.908
scrutinised and lessons
must always be learned.

3853920473
03:02:53.909 --> 03:02:56.570
But but I wouldn't want us
to be in a position where

742565793
