confidence within policing,

1288441550
03:03:11.924 --> 03:03:14.582
but that is why we have
the independent arrangements

2479899
03:03:14.583 --> 03:03:17.765
that we do with the Iopc
to investigate fully,

1022441540
03:03:17.766 --> 03:03:20.324
to make findings of fact,
that then the government

996802495
03:03:20.324 --> 03:03:22.711
and others can take
action on Harpreet Uppal.

240191165
03:03:22.712 --> 03:03:25.058
>> Thank you, Madam Deputy Speaker.

1621174359
03:03:25.059 --> 03:03:27.966
Henry Nowak murder was
a senseless evil act,

226363872
03:03:27.967 --> 03:03:31.515
a criminal act that Vickrum
Digwa bears responsibility for,

3990146139
03:03:31.516 --> 03:03:35.467
that he provided false claims to
evade responsibility is horrific.

932621909
03:03:35.962 --> 03:03:39.812
The actions of the perpetrator do
not represent a whole community.

1704073017
03:03:39.813 --> 03:03:43.260
And I know the Sikh community
in the UK wholly condemn it.

1228285060
03:03:43.261 --> 03:03:46.119
Many of us are deeply distressed
about the circumstances

1306396399
03:03:46.119 --> 03:03:48.979
of Henry's death and his
treatment in the final moments.

152792491
03:03:48.980 --> 03:03:51.639
So how will the Secretary
of State ensure that those

919620552
03:03:51.960 --> 03:03:54.315
lessons are learned
and that Henry's families,

4108680645
03:03:54.317 --> 03:03:58.121
Henry's family, are put first
and fully considered and on knife crime?

2236524184
03:03:58.122 --> 03:04:01.333
How will we ensure that the root
causes are dealt with and that

2125029129
03:04:01.335 --> 03:04:05.116
resources are provided to
agencies but also communities?

3233468337
03:04:05.117 --> 03:04:07.475
>> Home Secretary well,
let me assure her that

3973403277
03:04:07.476 --> 03:04:09.432
the Knife Crime Action Plan is funded,

617181710
03:04:09.433 --> 03:04:12.663
and we have put significant
money behind violence

1125994714
03:04:12.664 --> 03:04:14.418
reduction units and other measures

1523245683
03:04:14.419 --> 03:04:16.661
that we know are absolutely imperative in

336326364
03:04:16.662 --> 03:04:18.717
dealing with knife crime in our country.

2154614600
03:04:19.085 --> 03:04:21.092
And let me assure her again, as soon as

317043419
03:04:21.094 --> 03:04:22.948
the IOPC investigation is concluded,

1909545272
03:04:22.949 --> 03:04:24.906
I will make sure the House is updated.

450131288
03:04:24.907 --> 03:04:30.166
>> Sir Julian Lewis is it normal
police practice to handcuff a person

3566119169
03:04:30.167 --> 03:04:37.561
lying helpless on the ground
and clearly offering no resistance,

995322563
03:04:37.562 --> 03:04:42.266
and given her admirable
and utter rejection of differential

1693453564
03:04:42.267 --> 03:04:46.561
treatment of people
according to their race,

1683265206
03:04:46.562 --> 03:04:50.512
will she undertake to examine and withdraw

797663574
03:04:50.512 --> 03:04:52.517
the policing policy document identified

1376639268
03:04:52.518 --> 03:04:55.873
by the shadow Home Secretary as embodying

3304128477
03:04:57.960 --> 03:04:59.913
precisely such differential treatment?

763106899
03:04:59.914 --> 03:05:02.873
>> Secretary well, let me say to him,

646865832
03:05:02.874 --> 03:05:06.364
on policing practice and
the specifics of this case,

1898313401
03:05:06.365 --> 03:05:09.168
that is precisely what
the Iopc is looking at,

4075084470
03:05:09.169 --> 03:05:12.208
because they take into
account context and what

851034161
03:05:12.210 --> 03:05:14.664
the expectations of police officers are,

3752738412
03:05:14.665 --> 03:05:19.267
given the specific contexts of
danger that they that they face.

2252343789
03:05:19.268 --> 03:05:21.175
And the Iopc will look into that once

2778559878
03:05:21.176 --> 03:05:23.260
they've made their findings of fact.

3872552294
03:05:23.261 --> 03:05:25.268
I will, of course, return to the House.

3079576431
03:05:25.269 --> 03:05:30.122
And let me say again, look, on
the issue of differential treatment,

1132518059
03:05:30.123 --> 03:05:33.410
he will know he is a member of
long standing in this House.

1981168900
03:05:33.411 --> 03:05:38.613
We have had many debates where from
the opposite end of the spectrum,

2928011320
03:05:38.614 --> 03:05:40.070
if I might put it like that.

1836625582
03:05:40.071 --> 03:05:43.011
Today we are talking primarily about what

1090010181
03:05:43.012 --> 03:05:45.460
the white community in this instance.

49842755
03:05:45.461 --> 03:05:49.212
But there have been many debates
in this House about differential

2864713473
03:05:49.213 --> 03:05:51.418
treatment for minority
communities as well.

4149694196
03:05:51.419 --> 03:05:54.114
It's why I say I don't think
it's helpful for us to

2318032800
03:05:54.115 --> 03:05:56.521
look at this through
a community specific lens.

2266355122
03:05:56.523 --> 03:05:58.028
It is much broader than that.

998896173
03:05:58.029 --> 03:06:00.789
I will, of course, make sure
that I always engage with

1374256237
03:06:00.790 --> 03:06:04.458
the police on the specifics
of their policies,

4064671597
03:06:04.460 --> 03:06:08.012
but it is not my view that
the police are institutionally or

3598264085
03:06:08.014 --> 03:06:10.970
systemically operating a system
of differential treatment,

3918585527
03:06:10.971 --> 03:06:13.831
and we will always make sure
that we guard against that,

1380012774
03:06:13.832 --> 03:06:17.094
and I will work with the police
to make sure that never happens.

1297494259
03:06:17.095 --> 03:06:20.410
>> Toby Perkins well, thank you
very much, Deputy Speaker.

2404819460
03:06:20.411 --> 03:06:24.568
I welcome the Home Secretary's fierce
rejection of two tier policing,

3276081911
03:06:24.569 --> 03:06:27.410
or any suggestion that
people should be judged

3051420449
03:06:27.411 --> 03:06:30.771
differently according to their colour.

3619567685
03:06:30.771 --> 03:06:34.063
The footage that we saw was
one of the most sickening

1398510617
03:06:34.064 --> 03:06:36.071
things that I've ever seen in my heart.

1498121040
03:06:36.072 --> 03:06:40.815
Goes out to the Nowak family, who had
to witness that she's absolutely

3621037336
03:06:40.815 --> 03:06:44.271
right to say that we must wait
for the Iopc investigation,

2257532158
03:06:44.965 --> 03:06:49.464
but if it does turn out
that some kind of misguided

2556077514
03:06:49.465 --> 03:06:51.420
application of the culture of policing

3585567689
03:06:51.421 --> 03:06:54.819
has led to the victim being not believed

905436946
03:06:54.820 --> 03:06:57.112
while the murderer was believed,

3734518622
03:06:57.113 --> 03:07:00.119
what more will she be able
to do to make sure that

3670673090
03:07:00.121 --> 03:07:02.578
every single police officer
hears loud and clear

3819642611
03:07:02.579 --> 03:07:05.086
her message that everyone
deserves to be policed,

4053872990
03:07:05.087 --> 03:07:07.092
regardless of the colour of their skin?

3705243489
03:07:07.094 --> 03:07:08.348
In exactly the same way?

2243848511
03:07:08.349 --> 03:07:10.766
>> Secretary well, let me give my hon.

3566475031
03:07:10.767 --> 03:07:14.268
Friend that assurance that as soon as

4225536934
03:07:14.269 --> 03:07:16.574
the Iopc investigation
has concluded and they

405132036
03:07:16.576 --> 03:07:18.582
have made their findings in relation to

2692388498
03:07:18.583 --> 03:07:20.637
the specific circumstances of this case,

2191334328
03:07:20.639 --> 03:07:24.253
I will make sure we return to this
House so that we have an opportunity

3714061475
03:07:24.253 --> 03:07:27.719
to debate collectively what
the correct response will be,

362577319
03:07:27.720 --> 03:07:30.178
but let me just reassure
him and everybody else.

3602960749
03:07:30.179 --> 03:07:34.378
I will never stand for a system
where there is any suggestion

383505033
03:07:34.378 --> 03:07:36.484
of differential treatment before the law.

1436084309
03:07:36.485 --> 03:07:39.396
We are all equal before
the law, and every lesson that we

1360582754
03:07:39.396 --> 03:07:42.055
learn must always live up
to that abiding principle.

3032204759
03:07:42.056 --> 03:07:44.161
>> Suella Braverman Madam Deputy Speaker.

2132437548
03:07:44.162 --> 03:07:45.820
>> Henry Nowak was.

1092347672
03:07:45.821 --> 03:07:46.723
>> Murdered near.

3210478448
03:07:46.724 --> 03:07:49.431
>> My constituency of Fareham
and Waterlooville, and.

2612863164
03:07:49.432 --> 03:07:50.284
>> Local people.

523993447
03:07:50.285 --> 03:07:52.860
>> Are rightly furious
with Hampshire police.

3393403687
03:07:52.862 --> 03:07:57.669
Those officers who attended the scene,
but also those leading the force.

620816318
03:07:57.670 --> 03:08:03.364
It's important to remember that Henry's
murderer accused him of racism.

441838864
03:08:03.365 --> 03:08:05.020
And in honour of Henry's legacy,

514362166
03:08:05.021 --> 03:08:08.119
it's important that we're
all abundantly clear.

3857194695
03:08:08.119 --> 03:08:13.314
The judge found absolutely zero
evidence to back up that claim.

3147415436
03:08:13.315 --> 03:08:17.821
Does the Home Secretary agree
that a false accusation

1169964905
03:08:17.822 --> 03:08:21.615
of racism against a white
person is just as bad,

3492697104
03:08:21.616 --> 03:08:26.925
if not worse, than a legitimate claim
of racism because of the deceit?

2568717369
03:08:26.926 --> 03:08:29.785
Does she also agree that
watching that body cam footage,

1423828493
03:08:29.786 --> 03:08:32.822
it is clear that police officers treated

4029607893
03:08:32.823 --> 03:08:36.219
Henry with disdain and contempt
and arguably negligence

3030309791
03:08:36.960 --> 03:08:38.716
because of the colour of his skin?

104527260
03:08:38.717 --> 03:08:43.673
We are hearing number ten say that
two tier policing does not exist.

1844508381
03:08:43.964 --> 03:08:46.320
Home Secretary, where is
the leadership today?

3293055764
03:08:46.964 --> 03:08:48.367
British people are furious.

4024486468
03:08:48.368 --> 03:08:50.875
The leadership is not
coming from the government.

2818899543
03:08:50.876 --> 03:08:51.679
>> Do you hear?

74291051
03:08:51.960 --> 03:08:52.912
>> Home Secretary?

1401344252
03:08:52.913 --> 03:08:55.121
>> Let me say I disagree
with her entirely.

3101312062
03:08:55.122 --> 03:08:57.779
I think that good leadership
in these circumstances,

1225288840
03:08:57.780 --> 03:08:59.132
actually great leadership,

379953706
03:08:59.133 --> 03:09:02.619
has already been shown by
the family of Henry Nowak in the tenor

1573983564
03:09:02.621 --> 03:09:05.429
of their response and their
statement and their desire,

3455255684
03:09:05.430 --> 03:09:08.165
rightly, in my view, to not
see this murder be used

2272669943
03:09:08.166 --> 03:09:12.217
as a tool of furthering
division in our country.

4274620528
03:09:12.217 --> 03:09:17.121
And I think we could all do well to
take our lead from Henry's family.

1680354380
03:09:17.122 --> 03:09:20.426
But let me also say to her,
I am in the house today.

96432791
03:09:20.427 --> 03:09:21.679
I'm answering questions.

2938969121
03:09:21.680 --> 03:09:23.519
I've undertaken to come back.

3751186789
03:09:23.520 --> 03:09:25.675
Once the IOPC investigation has concluded.

3994571148
03:09:25.967 --> 03:09:26.217
She.

1632875027
03:09:26.219 --> 03:09:27.824
She is a former home secretary.

547758318
03:09:27.824 --> 03:09:32.515
She will know these independent
arrangements exist so that people can

1988422292
03:09:32.516 --> 03:09:35.978
have confidence in the findings that
are made in cases such as this,

2942088510
03:09:35.979 --> 03:09:38.437
and to know that they are
done without political

2320010993
03:09:38.438 --> 03:09:41.966
interference or for political ends.

3509035605
03:09:41.967 --> 03:09:45.079
Let me say to her on the broader
question point that she made

674503730
03:09:45.080 --> 03:09:47.838
at the start of her contribution
on false allegations.

2318256140
03:09:47.839 --> 03:09:50.619
Lies are lies, and they
must be called out as such.

3079559903
03:09:50.621 --> 03:09:52.364
And we're allies.

693973742
03:09:52.365 --> 03:09:54.520
Criminal or criminal leads to criminality.

31744806
03:09:54.521 --> 03:09:56.824
It must face the full force of the law.

458360948
03:09:56.826 --> 03:09:59.322
That is what has happened in this case.

1871801023
03:09:59.323 --> 03:10:02.634
There has been a measure of justice
because the criminal case has

3764560543
03:10:02.963 --> 03:10:06.360
concluded and the murderer has
been found guilty of murder,

2059206231
03:10:06.360 --> 03:10:08.969
and the judge has made
further findings in relation

1803033707
03:10:08.970 --> 03:10:10.725
to the circumstances of this case.

2776021790
03:10:10.967 --> 03:10:13.177
And again, I would urge
her and some of her

1080855271
03:10:13.178 --> 03:10:15.233
colleagues when commenting on this case.

3526669664
03:10:15.234 --> 03:10:18.024
They stick to the facts as
they have been established.

3644300661
03:10:18.025 --> 03:10:19.669
>> Jas Athwal thank.

2810028648
03:10:19.670 --> 03:10:21.174
>> You, Madam Deputy Speaker,

1282768354
03:10:21.175 --> 03:10:25.268
and can I thank the Home
Secretary and the Shadow

2313238095
03:10:25.269 --> 03:10:30.775
Home Secretary for the way they
introduced this very sensitive issue.

535344329
03:10:30.776 --> 03:10:36.222
The murder of Henry Nowak was
a wicked act of brutality.

152293534
03:10:36.223 --> 03:10:36.975
His >> Family.

3714213306
03:10:36.976 --> 03:10:37.578
>> And all.

634449958
03:10:37.579 --> 03:10:40.890
>> Those who loved him have been
left with an unimaginable grief,

2451466076
03:10:40.891 --> 03:10:42.092
mourning their brother,

1090094036
03:10:43.967 --> 03:10:48.720
their son and their friend, who
they'll never, ever get back.

1721488409
03:10:48.721 --> 03:10:52.715
I know members across
the House share my devastation

2385517412
03:10:52.716 --> 03:10:56.821
at this vile murder by
this vile individual.

2445666912
03:10:56.822 --> 03:10:59.222
However, some members have been using

722178247
03:10:59.223 --> 03:11:01.428
the horrific incident
as political capital,

4256401159
03:11:02.981 --> 03:11:05.235
spreading disinformation
for their own gain.

2384340183
03:11:05.237 --> 03:11:09.073
Does the Home Secretary
agree that politicians

2703720462
03:11:09.074 --> 03:11:11.771
have a responsibility to act with decorum,

2910398890
03:11:11.773 --> 03:11:15.472
to focus on Henry, who lost his
life and his grieving family,

3797419420
03:11:16.974 --> 03:11:18.479
who've lost a son, a brother?

1838477822
03:11:18.480 --> 03:11:19.332
Rather than fan.

2789613956
03:11:20.965 --> 03:11:22.920
The flames of Division Home Secretary.

1771817423
03:11:22.921 --> 03:11:24.619
>> I agree with my hon.

1842907772
03:11:24.621 --> 03:11:27.118
Friend and I do believe on this matter we

1956489740
03:11:27.119 --> 03:11:29.225
should take our lead from Henry's family,

3706330551
03:11:29.922 --> 03:11:32.633
who I think have set
an example for us all to follow.

3805387920
03:11:34.967 --> 03:11:36.071
>> Doctor Luke Evans.

328285131
03:11:36.072 --> 03:11:37.175
>> I've been stabbed.

749422529
03:11:38.967 --> 03:11:40.472
Versus he racially abused me.

1338307059
03:11:40.473 --> 03:11:45.027
How's the government going to rebuild
public confidence in our culture

790713284
03:11:45.028 --> 03:11:47.033
and institutions that attempted to rank

3313628231
03:11:47.034 --> 03:11:49.526
people by their perceived oppression,

1228585794
03:11:49.527 --> 03:11:53.473
rather than judging each person on
their own actions and the reality.

2043392908
03:11:53.967 --> 03:11:54.519
Very good.

1427552581
03:11:54.520 --> 03:11:55.221
>> Secretary.

1559869774
03:11:55.222 --> 03:11:57.923
>> Well, let me just repeat to the hon.

3183943822
03:11:57.924 --> 03:12:01.381
Gentleman the point I've
already made in this debate.

3190656033
03:12:01.382 --> 03:12:06.375
There can be no suggestion of two
tier policing in our country,

1789569217
03:12:06.376 --> 03:12:08.372
and the vast majority of cases,

1129643635
03:12:08.373 --> 03:12:11.383
the police apply the law fairly
and without fear or favour,

2022177002
03:12:11.384 --> 03:12:12.789
and they must always do so.

4217857177
03:12:12.790 --> 03:12:15.514
Once the Iopc investigation has concluded,

3427785587
03:12:15.515 --> 03:12:17.271
I will make sure that the specific

1014385415
03:12:17.271 --> 03:12:21.175
lessons from the circumstances of
this case are learned and acted upon.

3291509351
03:12:21.176 --> 03:12:22.931
>> Calvin Bailey thank you, Madam.

1136579793
03:12:22.967 --> 03:12:23.920
>> Deputy Speaker.

1080298975
03:12:23.921 --> 03:12:27.576
This crime was a vile act and
a crime of the utmost severity,

733053764
03:12:27.577 --> 03:12:30.688
and I'm pleased that it's been
treated as such by our courts.

2102621921
03:12:30.929 --> 03:12:33.239
This is a case about
a murder of a young man,

3959834572
03:12:33.240 --> 03:12:36.574
and our thoughts should remain
with Henry Nowak family.

3412360086
03:12:37.967 --> 03:12:40.527
We do not know why
the officers acted as they did,

4112429505
03:12:41.967 --> 03:12:46.172
but there is nothing in the Macpherson
inquiry that can be blamed upon

2203253132
03:12:46.173 --> 03:12:50.579
the apparent lack of humanity displayed
in the body worn camera footage.

756602773
03:12:50.972 --> 03:12:54.717
Does the Home Secretary agree
with me that we should reflect

985360525
03:12:54.719 --> 03:12:57.569
upon the words of Henry's
father, Mark Nowak,

2974434540
03:12:57.570 --> 03:13:00.530
who asked that his son's
death should not be used

913325026
03:13:00.531 --> 03:13:04.771
to create further division,
hatred or tension?

1477070801
03:13:04.773 --> 03:13:07.983
And does she agree that this is
entirely what the interventions

42585074
03:13:07.984 --> 03:13:11.126
of the member of Clacton
and others seek to do?

1015842388
03:13:11.127 --> 03:13:12.079
>> Home Secretary.

1837887991
03:13:13.966 --> 03:13:14.920
>> I thank my hon.

2843118075
03:13:14.921 --> 03:13:16.374
Friend for his contribution.

816442104
03:13:16.375 --> 03:13:17.621
Let me say I do.

3308880547
03:13:17.622 --> 03:13:18.676
I do agree with him.

786523465
03:13:18.677 --> 03:13:18.976
He's.

4198068258
03:13:18.978 --> 03:13:22.327
He's right to refer to
the words of Henry's father.

1931233522
03:13:23.964 --> 03:13:27.524
Many members have received have
referred to those words rightly today,

645334268
03:13:27.525 --> 03:13:30.222
and it is something that we
should all bear in mind.

77599016
03:13:30.223 --> 03:13:31.677
Let me just reiterate again.

692075143
03:13:32.967 --> 03:13:35.929
I will ensure that all of
the lessons that must be learned

2763829714
03:13:35.930 --> 03:13:40.020
from this case are learned
and are acted upon properly,

2110805995
03:13:40.021 --> 03:13:43.823
but this case must turns on its own
facts and its own circumstances,

3621771968
03:13:43.824 --> 03:13:46.374
and is not to be used, in my view,

3031850351
03:13:46.375 --> 03:13:49.177
to unwind other changes
that were made in order

88109177
03:13:49.178 --> 03:13:52.165
to rebuild public confidence in policing.

4084690908
03:13:52.166 --> 03:13:52.717
>> Thomas.

4198198419
03:13:52.717 --> 03:13:53.570
>> Madam Deputy.

1621251239
03:13:53.967 --> 03:13:54.569
>> Speaker.

149717636
03:13:54.570 --> 03:13:55.974
>> This cowardly murder is.

1618214540
03:13:55.975 --> 03:13:58.081
Not a reflection upon the Sikh community,

1926772935
03:13:58.082 --> 03:14:04.170
which has integrated itself with
honour and modesty into the UK.

1846907943
03:14:04.171 --> 03:14:06.226
I understand that the weapon wielded was

4181106978
03:14:07.971 --> 03:14:10.026
not that traditionally carried by Sikhs.

476541731
03:14:10.027 --> 03:14:15.280
I am, however, I, however,
believe that this murder

2155750383
03:14:15.281 --> 03:14:19.126
may give reasonable grounds
to review existing

1215159069
03:14:21.161 --> 03:14:23.517
exemptions to knife
legislation on the grounds

3451199216
03:14:23.518 --> 03:14:25.833
of religious reasons and national dress.

730444822
03:14:25.833 --> 03:14:28.425
I know that the Home
Secretary wants to half

3079384053
03:14:28.426 --> 03:14:30.382
knife crime within the next ten years.

2796136043
03:14:30.383 --> 03:14:33.271
What message do these exemptions give?

590281765
03:14:33.273 --> 03:14:38.770
Is she honestly going to
rule out at least a review?

2667633229
03:14:38.771 --> 03:14:39.723
>> Home Secretary.

251535690
03:14:39.724 --> 03:14:42.026
>> Well, let me just say to the hon.

3359833372
03:14:42.027 --> 03:14:46.429
Gentleman, as I as I've said
earlier in this debate,

3096625618
03:14:46.430 --> 03:14:49.489
our religious freedoms and
the arrangements we have are long

1585398573
03:14:49.490 --> 03:14:52.499
standing and have been designed
to strike the right balance

2107201744
03:14:52.972 --> 03:14:55.427
between religious freedom
and public protection.

917999110
03:14:55.972 --> 03:14:57.979
I have said earlier in this debate that

2825549188
03:14:57.980 --> 03:15:01.583
the wider question is something that

1292915042
03:15:01.583 --> 03:15:05.046
is worthy of serious consideration,
which is what I will give to it,

729208874
03:15:05.047 --> 03:15:07.003
but I would want to start that process

1803315928
03:15:07.005 --> 03:15:09.726
by discussing with the Sikh community

711886872
03:15:09.726 --> 03:15:11.873
themselves to knife crime campaigners

218943553
03:15:11.874 --> 03:15:14.625
and also the police about this matter.

3024109617
03:15:14.626 --> 03:15:16.734
That I think is the right way to proceed,

3286433231
03:15:16.735 --> 03:15:18.690
rather than launching a formal review.

1940277672
03:15:18.973 --> 03:15:21.531
Because actually, as
the judge found in this case,

2671450376
03:15:21.532 --> 03:15:23.974
this was not an act of
religious observance.

3162310127
03:15:23.975 --> 03:15:24.275
What?

1868893591
03:15:24.276 --> 03:15:26.734
The minute that knife was
unsheathed to be used,

1054847891
03:15:26.735 --> 03:15:28.176
it became a murder weapon.

1031387001
03:15:28.177 --> 03:15:31.088
And the murderer has now faced
the full force of the law.

1593701760
03:15:31.089 --> 03:15:31.841
>> Alex Baker.

383468697
03:15:31.972 --> 03:15:33.426
>> Thank you, Madam Speaker.

4073879511
03:15:33.427 --> 03:15:36.928
My thoughts are with the family
and friends of Henry Nowak.

3357939918
03:15:36.929 --> 03:15:41.080
It was absolutely gut
wrenching to see the video

18737798
03:15:41.081 --> 03:15:44.730
footage of the body worn
camera in Hampshire.

1528179083
03:15:44.731 --> 03:15:48.576
This murder has left
people deeply shocked,

2849685837
03:15:48.577 --> 03:15:51.227
not only by the violence of the act,

47782842
03:15:51.228 --> 03:15:54.674
but by the circumstances as he lay dying.

35051357
03:15:54.675 --> 03:15:57.473
I'm pleased to hear
that the Iopc will have

2957112116
03:15:57.474 --> 03:16:00.581
the resources they need
to fully investigate,

3700201941
03:16:00.582 --> 03:16:02.840
and I'm also glad to
hear that the Hampshire

164001274
03:16:02.841 --> 03:16:04.796
Police and Crime Commissioner has said

3054679456
03:16:04.797 --> 03:16:07.727
that she will ensure
that those those those

149898006
03:16:08.972 --> 03:16:10.925
recommendations are fully implemented.

3532497697
03:16:10.926 --> 03:16:12.580
Mistakes have clearly been made,

3017491182
03:16:12.581 --> 03:16:15.540
but will the Home Secretary
ensure that Hampshire and Isle

3862048232
03:16:15.541 --> 03:16:18.925
of Wight Constabulary
receive any support needed

2310768183
03:16:18.926 --> 03:16:23.427
to implement the Iopc findings in full,

2368746012
03:16:23.428 --> 03:16:26.575
and that lessons on victim
recognition and officer

3603745207
03:16:26.576 --> 03:16:29.576
judgement and impartiality
are acted on swiftly.

1287252462
03:16:29.577 --> 03:16:31.685
>> Home Secretary yes, I can give my hon.

778967771
03:16:31.686 --> 03:16:33.441
Friend that assurance and in fact,

4207025401
03:16:33.442 --> 03:16:35.877
the Policing Minister met with the Police

3050625207
03:16:35.878 --> 03:16:37.933
and Crime Commissioner earlier on today.

765213326
03:16:37.934 --> 03:16:39.639
>> Shockat Adam thank you, Madam.

3688224474
03:16:39.640 --> 03:16:40.592
>> Deputy Speaker.

79168291
03:16:40.593 --> 03:16:43.955
We do not want Henry's murder to
be used to create further hatred,

3608880418
03:16:43.976 --> 03:16:45.028
division or tension.

252186729
03:16:45.029 --> 03:16:47.286
Those are the words of
a heartbroken father.

2292093547
03:16:47.287 --> 03:16:49.697
And I pray we all, all
heed them in this house.

265406296
03:16:49.698 --> 03:16:51.856
This is a heinous crime made all the worse

3325255574
03:16:51.857 --> 03:16:53.511
by the shocking police response.

2326064045
03:16:53.512 --> 03:16:55.125
And there must be lessons.

3896691425
03:16:55.126 --> 03:16:58.539
So can I ask the Home Secretary
what she is going to do differently

400904609
03:16:58.540 --> 03:17:00.848
to crack down on
the epidemic of knife crime,

2663713808
03:17:00.849 --> 03:17:03.004
possibly a dedicated knife crime Minister?

2269320533
03:17:03.005 --> 03:17:06.177
And what steps will she
take to ensure that

623527402
03:17:06.178 --> 03:17:08.776
our Sikh community overwhelmingly,

2721812663
03:17:08.777 --> 03:17:11.531
overwhelmingly peaceful
and overwhelmingly integrated,

1041182243
03:17:11.532 --> 03:17:15.093
are not held collectively responsible
by those that wish to divide us?

4037346764
03:17:15.094 --> 03:17:16.046
>> Home Secretary?

3105226611
03:17:16.047 --> 03:17:18.206
>> Let me just say to him, on knife crime,

2367006454
03:17:18.207 --> 03:17:21.266
the government has a landmark
commitment to halve the levels

1771218456
03:17:21.267 --> 03:17:23.926
of knife crime in this country
over the next decade.

3461217216
03:17:23.927 --> 03:17:26.234
We have our landmark
Knife Crime Action plan.

4027793955
03:17:26.235 --> 03:17:27.640
It is a funded action plan.

297465036
03:17:27.641 --> 03:17:31.893
The Prime Minister has taken
a personal interest in that commitment,

3107710813
03:17:31.894 --> 03:17:36.284
and this government will strain
every sinew to deliver on that.

826533130
03:17:36.285 --> 03:17:38.577
>> Graham Stringer thank you, Madam.

1373428385
03:17:38.578 --> 03:17:39.530
>> Deputy Speaker.

3731902126
03:17:39.531 --> 03:17:44.483
In the 80s and 90s in this country,
many police officers carried

3088683338
03:17:45.976 --> 03:17:48.484
out their duties in
a prejudicial and racist way.

2695726752
03:17:48.976 --> 03:17:51.082
And I'm proud, together with many others,

1069533670
03:17:51.083 --> 03:17:59.432
of having worked to eliminate
that racism as much as we could.

3346358732
03:17:59.433 --> 03:18:04.580
We are now left with maybe a more
difficult problem to deal with.

819961941
03:18:04.581 --> 03:18:10.233
Many police officers and other
public servants are now frightened

2919478405
03:18:12.977 --> 03:18:18.678
that they will be accused of racism
in carrying out those duties.

1675917799
03:18:18.679 --> 03:18:23.130
What action does the Home
Secretary think she can take and

287579281
03:18:23.131 --> 03:18:28.132
the Cabinet can take to reassure
people who are accused of racism?

4035670364
03:18:28.133 --> 03:18:30.587
The proper process will affect them,

1724537843
03:18:30.588 --> 03:18:34.880
and it won't just leave
them out of a job forever.

3314854145
03:18:34.881 --> 03:18:37.691
>> Home Secretary well, let
me say firstly that my hon.

3082233435
03:18:37.976 --> 03:18:42.978
Friend is right to remind the House
of the historic context in relation

2744851958
03:18:42.979 --> 03:18:47.832
to policing in this country and on
the question of of racism itself.

1417289349
03:18:47.833 --> 03:18:52.380
And many minority communities
have been on the receiving

179884747
03:18:52.381 --> 03:18:54.288
end of of that treatment in the past.

3842286144
03:18:54.289 --> 03:18:57.953
It is right that the system as a whole
has sought to learn those lessons

2379146650
03:18:57.954 --> 03:19:01.316
and to deliver a policing service
that we can all be confident in,

4092049430
03:19:01.317 --> 03:19:04.228
and to know that we are all
treated fairly under the law.

584431190
03:19:04.229 --> 03:19:07.591
That is what I will ensure continues
to be the case going forward.

3525723453
03:19:08.974 --> 03:19:11.583
I would say to him, on
the question of accusations,

3821351755
03:19:11.584 --> 03:19:12.937
when accusations are made,

489143606
03:19:12.938 --> 03:19:17.311
whether in a legal and policing
context or indeed throughout

2303229352
03:19:17.312 --> 03:19:20.021
other parts of the public
sector, they are just that.

3939187818
03:19:20.022 --> 03:19:21.124
They are accusations.

2047329385
03:19:21.125 --> 03:19:24.184
And we should remember
the principles of our broader justice

868815750
03:19:24.185 --> 03:19:28.233
system when it comes to innocence
and findings of guilt and

624506703
03:19:28.234 --> 03:19:32.529
the fairness of procedures to
give people a chance to explain

2724782245
03:19:32.530 --> 03:19:35.588
themselves without finding
the fact being made against them.

1630443402
03:19:35.589 --> 03:19:38.248
Before that has happened,
I would expect to see that

3733668222
03:19:38.249 --> 03:19:40.604
happen throughout
the criminal justice system,

1032804544
03:19:40.605 --> 03:19:42.761
but also throughout wider society as well.

2084514766
03:19:42.762 --> 03:19:43.614
>> Jim Allister.

1950549976
03:19:43.615 --> 03:19:45.226
>> Thank you.

1918336128
03:19:45.227 --> 03:19:51.680
>> When the race card was
played by his murderer,

2644322201
03:19:51.681 --> 03:19:57.732
was Henry Nowak treated differently
because of the colour of his skin,

732376504
03:19:57.733 --> 03:20:01.587
causing the innocent
victim to be handcuffed

1477598350
03:20:01.588 --> 03:20:07.627
and the murderer pandered to.

3297412415
03:20:07.628 --> 03:20:09.936
Secretary of State.
>> Well, the reaction of the police

2742636974
03:20:09.937 --> 03:20:11.943
officers who attended the scene to the.

1217369859
03:20:14.976 --> 03:20:18.882
The circumstances that they faced
is what the Iopc is investigating.

2111319355
03:20:18.883 --> 03:20:22.243
Once that investigation is complete
and findings of fact are made,

869007725
03:20:22.244 --> 03:20:24.501
I'll be happy to discuss
the further lessons

255288605
03:20:24.502 --> 03:20:26.258
with him and others in this House.

3424081681
03:20:26.259 --> 03:20:27.312
>> Chris Webb thank.

622025129
03:20:27.313 --> 03:20:28.416
>> You, Madam Deputy.

566927064
03:20:28.417 --> 03:20:29.571
>> Speaker and I join.

859332092
03:20:29.572 --> 03:20:31.176
>> Colleagues across the House.

2207701402
03:20:31.177 --> 03:20:33.534
>> Offering my thoughts
and prayers to Henry's

2666757301
03:20:33.535 --> 03:20:35.691
family for his vile and disgusting murder.

2900172193
03:20:35.692 --> 03:20:37.596
Unfortunately, we're seeing those far

1420138029
03:20:37.597 --> 03:20:39.452
right groups in Blackpool and across

3115019878
03:20:39.453 --> 03:20:42.780
the country using Henry's
death and weaponising

4230131484
03:20:42.781 --> 03:20:44.630
it to create more hatred.

2333230906
03:20:44.631 --> 03:20:46.788
So can Tom Secretary join me in condemning

2047617990
03:20:46.789 --> 03:20:48.945
those in Blackpool and across the country,

3344042638
03:20:48.982 --> 03:20:52.176
and make sure that we honour
the powerful call from his

3259279442
03:20:52.177 --> 03:20:57.882
family who don't want to be
used for further division,

1318210776
03:20:57.883 --> 03:21:00.386
hatred or, you know,
tension in this country.

2746199645
03:21:00.387 --> 03:21:00.687
Yeah.

1880913459
03:21:00.688 --> 03:21:02.395
>> Well, let me join with my hon.

4198319589
03:21:02.396 --> 03:21:04.953
Friend and members across
this House in condemning

25790165
03:21:04.954 --> 03:21:06.860
the actions of the far right utterly.

3053624536
03:21:06.861 --> 03:21:08.866
They are completely unacceptable and we

4108198860
03:21:08.867 --> 03:21:12.334
should all take a stand against them,

1739068324
03:21:12.335 --> 03:21:14.439
weaponising this, this horrifying murder,

4046759870
03:21:14.440 --> 03:21:17.581
this terrible tragedy for
the Nowak family in order to spread

995134405
03:21:17.582 --> 03:21:20.139
further division is not
what this moment requires.

1909913528
03:21:20.140 --> 03:21:23.502
And I hope that that can have broad
support from across the House.

1095080635
03:21:23.503 --> 03:21:24.957
>> Carla Lockhart thank you.

3409272648
03:21:24.958 --> 03:21:26.211
>> Madam Deputy Speaker.

2473845112
03:21:26.212 --> 03:21:28.017
My thoughts are with Henry Stanley.

1159162909
03:21:28.018 --> 03:21:29.824
As I listened to his dad yesterday,

1051234854
03:21:29.825 --> 03:21:33.833
I couldn't help but cry
myself at the loss that they

3729312906
03:21:33.834 --> 03:21:35.991
have suffered and the fact that that video

3509202508
03:21:35.992 --> 03:21:40.088
footage is etched on their mind forever.

3999544235
03:21:40.089 --> 03:21:44.280
Madam Deputy Speaker, it
appears in the UK we have

1188707148
03:21:44.281 --> 03:21:47.332
an undercurrent of
anti-white racism brewing.

459004494
03:21:47.333 --> 03:21:51.032
We see white people jailed for allegedly

1805981653
03:21:51.033 --> 03:21:53.330
inciting racial hatred on social media,

2043751710
03:21:53.331 --> 03:21:57.530
but members of other communities
not even prosecuted

1036406359
03:21:57.531 --> 03:21:59.585
for viciously attacking police officers.

775824276
03:21:59.935 --> 03:22:01.388
Henry Nowak deserved better.

2547295490
03:22:01.389 --> 03:22:04.183
He did not deserve to be attacked.

2358478083
03:22:04.184 --> 03:22:07.333
He did not deserve to spend
his final moments pleading

4657977
03:22:07.334 --> 03:22:11.049
for help and saying he could not breathe.

1533350376
03:22:11.050 --> 03:22:13.476
He did not deserve not to be believed.

1163917309
03:22:13.477 --> 03:22:15.384
Above all, he did not deserve to die.

3879956185
03:22:16.981 --> 03:22:21.033
Why did it take this government until
yesterday to speak out on this

2923221789
03:22:21.034 --> 03:22:26.734
matter whilst running to virtue
signal on many other cases?

1617635256
03:22:26.735 --> 03:22:31.494
Is the UK no longer
a safe place for people

2390492054
03:22:31.495 --> 03:22:33.781
like Henry Nowak Home Secretary?

889573415
03:22:33.782 --> 03:22:34.988
>> I do say to the hon.

4142400666
03:22:34.989 --> 03:22:36.944
Lady, the reason the government hasn't

582641367
03:22:36.945 --> 03:22:38.799
commented until yesterday is because

1049859215
03:22:38.800 --> 03:22:41.860
there was a criminal case that
was going through our courts,

2326740070
03:22:41.861 --> 03:22:44.985
members of this House and certainly
members of the government

2226021396
03:22:44.986 --> 03:22:47.744
are not commentators for
the purposes of social media.

3195238012
03:22:47.745 --> 03:22:51.306
They are Ministers of the Crown
and they must respect the independence

3140952821
03:22:51.307 --> 03:22:54.367
of our criminal justice system
and the ability of our courts

3531082881
03:22:54.368 --> 03:22:56.774
and our independent legal
processes to function

1169908917
03:22:56.775 --> 03:22:58.782
so that when findings of fact are made,

2971712574
03:22:58.783 --> 03:23:01.140
a conviction happens
and a sentence is passed.

4168040581
03:23:01.141 --> 03:23:04.299
It commands public confidence
across the whole country because

2779305768
03:23:04.300 --> 03:23:07.308
everyone knows it has not been
interfered with politically.

176808704
03:23:07.309 --> 03:23:10.119
It is an independent assessment
of the facts of a case.

2783000079
03:23:10.120 --> 03:23:12.328
And I would remind her
and all members that

1146068990
03:23:12.329 --> 03:23:14.335
that is the responsibility we all have,

1872483317
03:23:14.336 --> 03:23:16.394
and I would urge her to reflect on that.

3571534466
03:23:16.395 --> 03:23:19.083
>> Tom Rutland thank you,
Madam Deputy Speaker,

3958396358
03:23:19.084 --> 03:23:20.389
and I thank my right hon.

2855056532
03:23:20.390 --> 03:23:21.693
Friend for her statement.

3898519300
03:23:21.694 --> 03:23:24.403
And can I offer my condolences
to Henry Nowak family,

2286991577
03:23:24.404 --> 03:23:26.560
who have been through an appalling ordeal.

1786204253
03:23:26.561 --> 03:23:28.266
What assurances can my right hon.

2760460725
03:23:28.267 --> 03:23:31.876
Friend provide that Henry Nowak
families concerns regarding the initial

4148301409
03:23:31.877 --> 03:23:35.586
police response are being fully
considered by the relevant authorities,

3291819634
03:23:35.587 --> 03:23:38.495
that lessons will be learned
from this terrible incident,

1278421228
03:23:38.496 --> 03:23:41.608
so that no other family has to
see their loved one doubted in

3590948279
03:23:41.609 --> 03:23:44.684
their final moments by those
who should be helping them.

1697609324
03:23:44.685 --> 03:23:48.086
>> Home Secretary yes, let
me give that assurance

3967213649
03:23:48.087 --> 03:23:50.334
to him and through him to the family,

3193819472
03:23:50.335 --> 03:23:53.697
as I have done so earlier and in
particular in my statement today,

1998470289
03:23:53.698 --> 03:23:58.032
they asked a specific question of
me when they responded yesterday.

636823384
03:23:58.033 --> 03:24:00.040
And and, and I have met that challenge,

86368777
03:24:00.041 --> 03:24:02.199
and I will ensure we continue to meet that

3587696148
03:24:02.200 --> 03:24:04.206
challenge and that they get the answers

4230806216
03:24:04.207 --> 03:24:06.113
that they need and that they deserve.

3655519141
03:24:06.114 --> 03:24:07.066
>> Final question.

2727382566
03:24:07.067 --> 03:24:07.918
Tristan Osborne.

249116324
03:24:07.919 --> 03:24:10.226
>> Thank you very much,
Madam Deputy Speaker.

3951948405
03:24:10.227 --> 03:24:12.686
And can I thank the Home
Secretary for coming to

3500663354
03:24:12.687 --> 03:24:15.245
the House today and can
also extend the sympathies

3850553291
03:24:15.246 --> 03:24:17.855
on behalf of my constituents
to the family of Henry

3044779674
03:24:17.856 --> 03:24:20.264
Nowak and what is a heinous
and horrific crime?

1801292836
03:24:20.265 --> 03:24:21.969
There is speculation online about

1443184330
03:24:21.980 --> 03:24:24.035
the identities of these police officers,

40746022
03:24:24.036 --> 03:24:26.293
and it's also putting
other officers at risk

1617046000
03:24:26.294 --> 03:24:28.500
across the country due
to the irresponsible

642793640
03:24:28.501 --> 03:24:30.907
speculation of extreme
right groups and others,

1219514883
03:24:30.908 --> 03:24:34.134
which are fanning the flames of tension.

1819932904
03:24:34.135 --> 03:24:37.737
Can the Home Secretary confirm
to me what we are doing to

4148205710
03:24:37.738 --> 03:24:40.840
protect our officers on a daily
basis in regards to this,

1748383185
03:24:40.841 --> 03:24:43.397
and also comment on this
irresponsible speculation

687375682
03:24:43.398 --> 03:24:46.236
that is being undertaken online?

1902159194
03:24:46.237 --> 03:24:49.445
>> Home Secretary speculation
online is not just irresponsible,

562516595
03:24:49.446 --> 03:24:51.035
it is wholly unacceptable.

3342175685
03:24:51.036 --> 03:24:53.430
And as I said in my statement earlier,

725548819
03:24:53.431 --> 03:24:55.488
we should all take a stand against that.

1231095758
03:24:55.489 --> 03:24:59.892
It is putting people who are not
connected with this case at risk,

3094735747
03:24:59.893 --> 03:25:03.154
but also for the officers that
have been connected to this case.

2569680007
03:25:03.155 --> 03:25:06.789
There is a proper process that must
be allowed to take its course,

3356392075
03:25:06.790 --> 03:25:09.234
that will investigate
their conduct and make

1603323022
03:25:09.235 --> 03:25:11.441
the appropriate findings
in the proper way.

1139913146
03:25:11.980 --> 03:25:13.485
We should all, in this House,

2115307289
03:25:13.486 --> 03:25:15.843
stand up for the independence
of that process,

3249499698
03:25:15.844 --> 03:25:19.356
the space for that process to conclude
so that once it has concluded,

1025417400
03:25:19.357 --> 03:25:24.430
we can debate thoroughly
