on several occasions

3217850049
03:56:32.831 --> 03:56:34.966
his wish to raise standards

920533234
03:56:34.967 --> 03:56:38.430
and we took him at his word,
so perhaps he could reassure the House.

395268508
03:56:38.431 --> 03:56:42.825
There's nothing in amendment 54
that would impede that process,

1460799365
03:56:42.826 --> 03:56:46.668
which would make it in any way
more difficult for military

1955778839
03:56:46.669 --> 03:56:51.168
tenants who are dissatisfied
to see their needs addressed.

3830395777
03:56:51.169 --> 03:56:53.617
Turning now to our own amendments.

3163473293
03:56:53.618 --> 03:56:56.226
Our amendment one relates
to those people who might

1613594159
03:56:56.227 --> 03:56:58.516
be eligible to be called up as reserves,

3703192448
03:56:58.517 --> 03:57:00.574
but who also perform work which is vital

1378798705
03:57:00.575 --> 03:57:02.630
to defence in their civilian employment.

3414787687
03:57:02.631 --> 03:57:05.691
During the Second World War,
people in such a situation were

1491922314
03:57:05.692 --> 03:57:08.666
generally referred to as working
in reserved occupations.

1779375925
03:57:08.667 --> 03:57:11.275
The essence of this amendment
is that the Secretary

2513208959
03:57:11.276 --> 03:57:13.032
of State should be able to define,

1903494981
03:57:13.033 --> 03:57:15.689
via regulations certain
categories of civilian work,

3308740304
03:57:15.690 --> 03:57:18.046
which would be classed
as reserve occupations,

4031651301
03:57:18.047 --> 03:57:20.354
and therefore should be
able to exempt people

1290907996
03:57:20.355 --> 03:57:23.569
in that category from being mobilised.

3082870428
03:57:23.570 --> 03:57:27.873
We still believe that that
is a practical suggestion,

184094372
03:57:27.874 --> 03:57:32.283
but I take the point that there
is already some power on

3819819101
03:57:32.284 --> 03:57:35.578
the statute book that will
allow Ministers to do that.

1055793235
03:57:39.016 --> 03:57:42.668
So I think we're halfway
there, so I won't therefore be

3967034888
03:57:42.669 --> 03:57:49.717
minded to press this amendment
later this evening.

1834343493
03:57:49.718 --> 03:57:53.179
The amendments two and three refer
to the topic of service personnel

4148266310
03:57:53.180 --> 03:57:56.620
